WEBVTT

00:28.162 --> 00:30.931
I HAVE BOGIES APPROACHING,
30 MILES,

00:30.998 --> 00:33.101
240 DEGREES.

00:33.167 --> 00:34.702
COME RIGHT 40.

00:39.373 --> 00:42.110
O.K., LET'S NOT GET
TOO ANXIOUS TODAY.

00:42.176 --> 00:45.113
THIS IS MARINES
AGAINST NAVY, 1-V-1.

00:45.179 --> 00:47.615
TRY NOT TO SHOOT DOWN
YOUR WINGMAN.

00:49.117 --> 00:50.318
WATCH OUT.

00:50.384 --> 00:52.953
WATCH OUT, SQUIDS.
I'M HOT TODAY.

00:53.020 --> 00:54.988
HA HA HA!

00:55.055 --> 00:57.425
HEY! HA HA HA!

00:57.491 --> 01:01.429
HA HA HA!
HA HA HA HA!

01:01.495 --> 01:04.331
O.K., MEECHUM,
CLOSE IT UP.

01:13.073 --> 01:16.644
I HAVE NAVY BEARING 120,
20 MILES.

01:16.710 --> 01:18.179
COME RIGHT 30,

01:18.246 --> 01:20.681
SPREADS A FIGHTING WING.

01:26.454 --> 01:28.156
NAVY 4,
I HAVE BOGIES CLOSING.

01:28.222 --> 01:30.791
18 MILES, 240 DEGREES.

01:30.858 --> 01:33.361
ROGER. I GOT 'EM.

01:45.573 --> 01:48.176
THEY MUST BE
UNDER THIS STUFF.

01:48.242 --> 01:50.211
IT'S BREAKING UP AHEAD.

02:04.758 --> 02:06.694
BOGIES 8 MILES.

02:06.760 --> 02:08.729
COME RIGHT 90.

02:19.340 --> 02:22.276
LEADER HAS TALLY.

02:22.343 --> 02:24.044
ONE O'CLOCK LOW.

02:24.111 --> 02:25.279
PREACHER HAS TALLY.

02:25.346 --> 02:27.648
O.K. FIGHT'S ON.
GO GET THEM.

02:36.290 --> 02:37.725
BUENOS DIAS,
RUSTPICKERS.

02:37.791 --> 02:39.393
[CHUCKLING]

02:41.229 --> 02:43.231
COME ON.
MAKE YOUR MOVE.

02:43.297 --> 02:45.233
LET'S SEE WHAT YOU GOT,
BUDDY.

02:45.299 --> 02:48.236
LET'S SEE IT.
LET'S SEE IT.

02:48.302 --> 02:49.737
NOT BAD.

02:49.803 --> 02:51.239
IT'S NOT BAD.

02:51.305 --> 02:53.641
[CHUCKLING]

02:53.707 --> 02:54.742
NOT BAD.

02:56.377 --> 02:58.579
YOU'D BETTER
KICK IT, NAVY.

03:04.618 --> 03:07.187
TOO LATE.
GOT YOU NOW, SUCKER.

03:07.255 --> 03:08.222
YOU WATCHING US,
LEADER?

03:08.289 --> 03:09.457
AFFIRMATIVE.

03:09.523 --> 03:12.059
AH, YES. HOLD STILL.

03:12.125 --> 03:13.261
SMILE.

03:13.327 --> 03:15.263
O.K. I TAKE A SHOT...

03:15.329 --> 03:18.399
RIGHT THERE.
BANG!

03:18.466 --> 03:20.634
RIGHT UP YOUR SIX,
RUSTPICKER.

03:20.701 --> 03:22.236
[CHUCKLING]

03:22.303 --> 03:24.638
THAT'S A KILL,
MEECHUM.

03:26.640 --> 03:29.910
O.K., O.K.
I GOT THIS GUY NAILED.

03:29.977 --> 03:32.913
PRESS HIM.
STAY WITH HIM.

03:32.980 --> 03:35.616
COMING UP FOR THE SHOT,

03:35.683 --> 03:39.219
AND COMING UP,
AND RIGHT, RIGHT...

03:39.287 --> 03:40.921
AHH.

03:40.988 --> 03:42.890
RIGHT THERE!

03:42.956 --> 03:44.292
HA HA! WHOO!

03:44.358 --> 03:46.059
BEAUTIFUL.
THAT'S A KILL.

03:46.126 --> 03:47.961
LOOKED GOOD, SWEETHEART.

03:48.028 --> 03:50.498
[HUMMING MARINE'S HYMN]

03:53.367 --> 03:54.668
O.K., O.K.,
YOU CLOWNS.

03:54.735 --> 03:57.305
KNOCK IT OFF.
THE FIGHT'S OVER.

03:57.371 --> 03:58.806
JOIN ON ME.

03:58.872 --> 04:01.509
[HUMMING CONTINUES]

04:12.786 --> 04:15.823
[SINGING
IN FOREIGN LANGUAGE]

04:15.889 --> 04:18.559
WHOO!

04:18.625 --> 04:20.528
WHOO!

04:35.409 --> 04:37.010
[EVERYONE SHOUTING]

04:41.715 --> 04:44.852
OUTSTANDING, GENTLEMEN!
ON YOUR FEET!

04:44.918 --> 04:47.220
[TAPPING GLASS]

04:47.287 --> 04:48.822
TO THE GREATEST MARINE
FIGHTER PILOT

04:48.889 --> 04:52.159
THAT EVER CRAPPED
BETWEEN TWO SHOES.

04:52.225 --> 04:54.862
SOME OF YOU KNOW HIM
BY HIS NOM DE GUERRE...

04:54.928 --> 04:56.296
THE GREAT SANTINI.

04:56.364 --> 04:58.399
SOME OF YOU KNOW HIM
BY NAMES TOO FOUL

04:58.466 --> 05:02.770
TO BE REPEATED
OUTSIDE OF THIS AUGUST COMPANY.

05:02.836 --> 05:05.072
HERE'S TO OUR VICTORY TODAY
OVER NAVY.

05:05.138 --> 05:06.407
[LOUD CHEERING]

05:06.474 --> 05:08.409
HERE'S
TO HIS NEW ASSIGNMENT

05:08.476 --> 05:11.111
AS COMMANDER
OF THE 312 SQUADRON.

05:11.178 --> 05:14.648
I GIVE YOU BULL MEECHUM!

05:14.715 --> 05:17.451
SENORES, SENORES!
POR FAVOR!

05:17.518 --> 05:18.752
THE NOISE IS TOO MUCH,
YOU KNOW?

05:18.819 --> 05:20.220
THE OTHER GUESTS COMPLAIN.
PLEASE, HUH?

05:20.287 --> 05:21.655
OH, DEARIE.

05:21.722 --> 05:24.358
THEY DON'T LIKE TO HEAR US
THROW GLASSES?

05:24.425 --> 05:25.859
NO, SENOR.

05:25.926 --> 05:27.361
MARINES!

05:27.428 --> 05:29.397
HAROOGA!
HAROOGA!

05:30.431 --> 05:31.665
BEAT IT!

05:31.732 --> 05:34.167
MAYBE WE SHOULD
HOLD IT DOWN.

05:34.234 --> 05:36.504
I'D HATE FOR YOU TO GET IN TROUBLE
YOUR LAST NIGHT IN SPAIN.

05:36.570 --> 05:40.273
THAT WOULD BE JUST
AWFUL, WOULDN'T IT?

05:40.340 --> 05:41.675
TO THE CORPS ELITE.

05:41.742 --> 05:43.711
TO THAT SPECIAL BREED
OF SKY DEVIL

05:43.777 --> 05:46.113
KNOWN AND FEARED
THROUGHOUT THE WORLD,

05:46.179 --> 05:48.015
THE MARINE DOGFIGHTER.

05:48.081 --> 05:50.017
TO THE BRAVEST MEN
WHO EVER LIVED.

05:50.083 --> 05:52.920
THERE'S NOT A FORCE
WHO COULD DEFEAT US,

05:52.986 --> 05:56.390
DENY US VICTORY,
OR INTERRUPT OUR DESTINY.

05:56.457 --> 05:57.758
MARINES!

05:57.825 --> 05:59.059
[CHEERING]

05:59.126 --> 06:01.629
TO VICTORY!

06:04.465 --> 06:05.699
WHO'S IN CHARGE HERE?

06:05.766 --> 06:08.769
HE IS, SIR.
RIGHT THROUGH THERE.

06:14.475 --> 06:16.410
WHAT'S WRONG
WITH THIS MAN?

06:16.477 --> 06:18.712
HE'S HAD THE FLU, SIR.
IT'S WEAKENED HIM.

06:18.779 --> 06:20.881
DON'T GET SMART
WITH ME, COLONEL.

06:20.948 --> 06:21.849
MY WIFE AND I

06:21.915 --> 06:23.316
AND THE OTHER
PEOPLE OUT THERE

06:23.383 --> 06:25.719
WOULD LIKE A QUIET,
PLEASANT DINNER,

06:25.786 --> 06:27.287
AND WE'D APPRECIATE
YOUR CLEARING OUT

06:27.354 --> 06:30.424
AND TAKING YOUR UNGENTLEMANLY
CONDUCT WITH YOU.

06:30.491 --> 06:33.360
SIR, THIS IS
A GOING-AWAY PARTY FOR ME.

06:33.427 --> 06:34.928
DRINK UP AND MOVE OUT.

06:34.995 --> 06:36.430
UH, YES, SIR.

06:36.497 --> 06:39.433
COULD WE HAVE
ONE LAST DRINK AT THE BAR

06:39.500 --> 06:40.367
IF WE PROMISE
TO BEHAVE, CAPTAIN?

06:40.434 --> 06:41.935
ONE.

06:42.002 --> 06:44.371
I DON'T WANT YOU ANYWHERE
NEAR AFTER THAT.

06:44.438 --> 06:46.640
THANK YOU, SIR.

06:48.375 --> 06:49.743
O.K., YOU SWEET,
YOUNG THINGS.

06:49.810 --> 06:52.746
I WANT YOU TO GO
OUT TO THE BAR

06:52.813 --> 06:54.448
AND ACT
LIKE PERFECT GENTLEMEN.

06:54.515 --> 06:56.450
YOU'LL SEE A FLOOR SHOW

06:56.517 --> 06:58.318
THAT'LL MAKE
MARINE CORPS HISTORY.

06:58.385 --> 07:00.454
BUTTON UP AND GO ON OUT.

07:00.521 --> 07:01.855
TWO OF YOU TAKE CARE
OF THE SKIPPER.

07:01.922 --> 07:03.056
THAT'S GOOD.

07:09.530 --> 07:11.665
ALL RIGHT, THERE.

07:13.033 --> 07:14.768
THERE YOU ARE.

07:14.835 --> 07:16.670
AFTER YOU,
COLONEL.

07:26.547 --> 07:28.982
[LAUGHTER]

07:37.858 --> 07:41.495
TO ALL SQUIDS
AND RUSTPICKERS...

07:41.562 --> 07:43.497
HAROOGA, HAROOGA,
HAROOGA!

07:43.564 --> 07:45.098
HAROOGA!

07:52.573 --> 07:55.509
CARE TO DANCE WITH THE
GREAT SANTINI, MA'AM?

07:55.576 --> 07:56.910
I DON'T, UH...

07:56.977 --> 07:57.811
DAVID. DAVID!

07:57.878 --> 08:00.313
GET YOUR HANDS
OFF MY WIFE!

08:00.380 --> 08:01.549
COLONEL!

08:27.507 --> 08:29.743
OH, MY GOD!

08:33.914 --> 08:35.948
CHOW DOWN ON ME,
HOGS.

08:51.231 --> 08:53.867
[IN UNISON]
HAIL MARY, FULL OF GRACE,
THE LORD IS WITH THEE.

08:53.934 --> 08:55.869
BLESSED ART THOU
AMONGST WOMEN

08:55.936 --> 08:57.905
AND BLESSED IS THE FRUIT
OF THY WOMB, JESUS.

08:57.971 --> 09:00.874
HOLY MARY, MOTHER OF GOD,
PRAY FOR US SINNERS

09:00.941 --> 09:03.744
NOW AND AT THE HOUR
OF OUR DEATH. AMEN.

09:04.812 --> 09:06.880
OH, IF DAD'S
PLANE CRASHED,

09:06.947 --> 09:08.582
WE'D NEVER
FORGIVE OURSELVES

09:08.649 --> 09:11.084
FOR NOT SAYING
THAT EXTRA HAIL MARY.

09:11.151 --> 09:12.419
STAND UP STRAIGHT, BEN.

09:12.485 --> 09:13.887
COME ON. DON'T SLOUCH.
THAT'S IT.

09:13.954 --> 09:15.889
I DON'T WANT TO LEAVE
GRANDMA'S HOUSE.

09:15.956 --> 09:18.291
I WANT TO STAY
HERE IN ATLANTA.

09:18.358 --> 09:19.993
WE'LL BE BACK
TO VISIT.

09:20.060 --> 09:22.029
THAT'S WHAT YOU SAID
ABOUT CHERRY POINT.

09:22.095 --> 09:23.931
WE'LL BE BACK
TO CHERRY POINT AS WELL.

09:23.997 --> 09:26.634
THAT'S WHAT YOU TOLD KAREN
WHEN WE LEFT CAMP LEJEUNE.

09:26.700 --> 09:28.902
DON'T SPREAD DISSENSION,
MARY ANNE.

09:28.969 --> 09:31.538
I WANT DAD'S HOMECOMING
PERFECT, DO YOU HEAR?

09:31.605 --> 09:33.641
WANT ME
TO PUNCH HER, MOM?

09:33.707 --> 09:35.676
THEY'LL BURY YOU
IN A MATCHBOX.

09:35.743 --> 09:37.144
DID YOU HEAR THAT?

09:37.210 --> 09:38.846
MARY ANNE, STOP IT.

09:38.912 --> 09:40.748
I DON'T KNOW WHY
MATTHEW'S SO SENSITIVE.

09:40.814 --> 09:42.449
HE'S PRACTICALLY A GIANT
FOR A MIDGET.

09:42.515 --> 09:43.884
MAMMA!

09:43.951 --> 09:46.419
MARY ANNE,
LET'S TAKE A WALK.

09:46.486 --> 09:48.856
THAT'S A SPLENDID IDEA.

09:48.922 --> 09:52.525
[MARY ANNE]
YOU KNOW, BENNY BOY,
I'VE BEEN THINKING LATELY.

09:52.592 --> 09:54.728
MIND AGAINST MIND,
I MAUL YOU EVERY TIME.

09:54.795 --> 09:58.431
JUST REMEMBER I COULD KNOCK
EVERY TOOTH OUT OF YOUR FACE,

09:58.498 --> 10:00.133
AND THERE'S VERY LITTLE
YOU CAN DO ABOUT IT.

10:00.200 --> 10:01.568
BIG, BRAVE JOCK.

10:01.635 --> 10:05.639
SO WHAT?
I'D GET YOU BACK.

10:05.706 --> 10:07.040
I'D STEAL
YOUR CLEARASIL.

10:07.107 --> 10:07.975
WITHIN 48 HOURS,

10:08.041 --> 10:09.743
YOUR PIMPLES
WOULD MULTIPLY SO FAST,

10:09.810 --> 10:12.646
YOU'D BE DEAD.

10:12.713 --> 10:14.214
THERE IT IS.

10:19.386 --> 10:20.654
THERE IT IS.

10:20.721 --> 10:22.322
HEY, MOM!

10:22.389 --> 10:23.824
THERE IT IS!

10:23.891 --> 10:25.659
OH, I SEE IT, SUGAR,
I SEE IT.

10:25.726 --> 10:26.927
GET IN LINE.

10:26.994 --> 10:28.829
HE'LL PROBABLY
HOLD INSPECTION.

10:28.896 --> 10:30.731
BEN, STAND UP STRAIGHT.

10:33.300 --> 10:36.603
GIRLS, CHECK YOUR HAIR.

10:36.670 --> 10:37.971
ALL RIGHT,
NOW, REMEMBER,

10:38.038 --> 10:40.107
WHEN HE GETS OFF,
WE WILL WALK...

10:40.173 --> 10:41.374
WALK, PLEASE...

10:41.441 --> 10:42.910
WALK TO MEET HIM,
HUH?

10:42.976 --> 10:44.845
I'LL GO FIRST, THEN THE GIRLS,
THEN THE BOYS.

10:44.912 --> 10:48.148
I'LL GIVE HIM A BIG JUICY,
AND THEN THE GIRLS,

10:48.215 --> 10:50.150
AND YOU BOYS
SHAKE HANDS FIRMLY

10:50.217 --> 10:52.252
AND SAY,
"WELCOME HOME, COLONEL."

10:55.723 --> 10:59.659
BETTER GET A CHAIR
FOR MATT TO STAND ON.

10:59.727 --> 11:01.228
YOU'RE GOING TO GET IT.

11:01.294 --> 11:02.796
MATTHEW!

11:02.863 --> 11:04.264
OH, FOR HEAVEN'S SAKES.

11:04.331 --> 11:06.433
STAND UP HERE AND LET ME
GET YOUR HAIR COMBED.

11:08.401 --> 11:09.870
ALL RIGHT. TAKE IT, NOW.

11:09.937 --> 11:11.839
HURRY UP. HURRY UP.

11:14.274 --> 11:18.779
STAND BY
FOR A FIGHTER PILOT!

11:18.846 --> 11:20.213
YA-HOO!

11:20.280 --> 11:20.948
AHH!

11:21.014 --> 11:23.116
[LAUGHING AND SCREAMING]

11:27.154 --> 11:28.388
OHH!

11:28.455 --> 11:30.090
HEY, HEY!

11:43.971 --> 11:47.107
I MISSED YOU, LIL.
I MISSED YOU.

11:47.174 --> 11:49.109
OH, YEAH?

11:49.176 --> 11:50.778
ME, TOO.

11:53.280 --> 11:56.416
DO YOU KNOW WHEN
THE WORST TIMES WERE?

11:56.483 --> 11:57.885
NO.

11:57.951 --> 12:00.420
IN THE MORNING,
JUST LIKE NOW,

12:00.487 --> 12:02.222
BEFORE THE KIDS GOT UP.

12:02.289 --> 12:08.595
OH, JUST LYING HERE
LISTENING TO THAT QUIET,

12:08.661 --> 12:10.163
STARING UP
AT THE CEILING...

12:10.998 --> 12:13.433
ACHING
FOR THE FEEL OF YOU.

12:15.368 --> 12:16.970
MMM.

12:18.305 --> 12:21.741
WE GOT A LOT OF
CATCHING UP TO DO, LADY.

12:21.809 --> 12:22.943
OH, MY.

12:23.010 --> 12:29.049
COLONEL, SIR,
I'M AT YOUR DISPOSAL.

12:29.116 --> 12:30.083
OH, MY...

12:32.452 --> 12:33.887
YOU'VE WAITED A LONG TIME

12:33.954 --> 12:35.722
FOR THIS COMMAND,
HAVEN'T YOU?

12:35.789 --> 12:37.390
TOO LONG.

12:37.457 --> 12:38.892
TOO LONG.

12:38.959 --> 12:41.895
I'M SO PROUD OF YOU.

12:41.962 --> 12:44.431
PROUD OF YOU.

12:44.497 --> 12:48.101
PROUD OF YOU.
YOU KNOW I AM.

12:50.470 --> 12:51.905
COLONEL, SIR...

12:51.972 --> 12:53.706
YOU THINK WE'D TRY
A LITTLE BIT

12:53.773 --> 12:55.843
OF THAT CATCHING UP NOW?

12:55.909 --> 12:57.177
WELL, HONEY,
SUGAR DUMPLING,

12:57.244 --> 13:00.280
BULL MEECHUM
DON'T TRY NOTHIN'.

13:00.347 --> 13:02.415
HE JUST DO.

13:03.316 --> 13:06.419
I KNOW THAT. OH!

13:09.857 --> 13:11.124
[ALARM BUZZES]

13:11.191 --> 13:12.225
OH, NO!

13:12.292 --> 13:17.230
FOR HEAVEN'S SAKES, BULL,
WHAT TIME IS IT?

13:17.297 --> 13:19.499
COME ON.
UP AND AT 'EM.

13:19.566 --> 13:21.134
I AM NOT GOING ANYWHERE
AT 3:00 IN THE MORNING.

13:21.201 --> 13:24.271
I WANT TO BE AT THE
AIR STATION BY 1600.

13:24.337 --> 13:28.775
COME BACK TO BED.
IT DOESN'T MAKE ANY SENSE.

13:28.842 --> 13:31.311
MOVING DAY!
LET'S GO, HOGS!

13:31.378 --> 13:33.580
EVERYBODY AT THE CAR
IN FIVE MINUTES!

13:33.646 --> 13:35.248
[MOANING AND WHINING]

13:35.315 --> 13:38.485
[BEN]
GREAT TO HAVE YOU HOME, DAD.

13:38.551 --> 13:41.821
♪ FIRST TO FIGHT
FOR RIGHT AND FREEDOM ♪

13:41.889 --> 13:44.858
♪ AND TO KEEP
OUR HONOR CLEAN ♪

13:44.925 --> 13:48.128
♪ WE ARE PROUD
TO CLAIM THE TITLE ♪

13:48.195 --> 13:51.331
♪ OF UNITED STATES MARINE ♪

13:53.100 --> 13:53.733
YAY!

13:53.800 --> 13:55.035
ALL RIGHT!

13:55.102 --> 13:57.470
WHAT'S THE NEXT SONG,
SPORTS FANS?

13:57.537 --> 13:58.471
DIXIE.

13:58.538 --> 14:00.073
WHAT A HORSESHIT SONG.

14:00.140 --> 14:00.974
WATCH YOUR LANGUAGE.

14:01.041 --> 14:02.342
YEAH!
YEAH!

14:02.409 --> 14:03.911
DIXIE'S
A LOSER'S SONG.

14:03.977 --> 14:05.112
SING SOMETHING ELSE.

14:05.178 --> 14:06.513
DIXIE!
NO!

14:06.579 --> 14:08.548
YOU SING DIXIE,
AND I'LL SING

14:08.615 --> 14:10.117
BATTLE HYMN
OF THE REPUBLIC.

14:10.183 --> 14:11.584
I'LL SING
A WINNER'S SONG.

14:11.651 --> 14:13.153
YOU SING A LOSER'S
SONG.

14:13.220 --> 14:15.855
IT'S NOT A LOSER'S SONG.

14:15.923 --> 14:18.758
♪ I WISH I WAS
IN THE LAND OF COTTON ♪

14:18.825 --> 14:21.061
♪ OLD TIMES THERE
ARE NOT FORGOTTEN ♪

14:21.128 --> 14:23.563
♪ HE IS TRAMPLING OUT
THE VINTAGE ♪

14:23.630 --> 14:25.765
♪ WHERE THE GRAPES
OF WRATH ARE STORED ♪

14:25.832 --> 14:30.170
♪ GLORY, GLORY,
HALLELUJAH ♪

14:30.237 --> 14:33.173
♪ GLORY, GLORY,
HALLELUJAH ♪

14:33.240 --> 14:37.277
♪ GLORY, GLORY,
HALLELUJAH... ♪

14:42.015 --> 14:43.783
HEY, BEN, WAKE UP.

14:43.850 --> 14:45.785
QUIT PRETENDING
YOU'RE ASLEEP.

14:45.852 --> 14:47.287
COME ON.

14:47.354 --> 14:49.289
I AM ASLEEP.

14:49.356 --> 14:51.291
LET'S TALK.

14:56.163 --> 14:59.299
WHAT DO YOU WANT
TO TALK ABOUT?

15:02.169 --> 15:04.804
THE WHITE SOX
WON YESTERDAY.

15:04.871 --> 15:06.106
OH.

15:06.173 --> 15:08.008
THAT'S GREAT, DAD.

15:17.184 --> 15:20.787
HEY, DAD, ARE YOU EVER
AFRAID WHEN YOU FLY?

15:20.853 --> 15:22.122
HELL, YES.

15:22.189 --> 15:25.125
THAT'S WHAT MAKES ME
SO DAMN GOOD.

15:25.192 --> 15:26.359
YOU'LL KNOW WHAT
I'M TALKING ABOUT

15:26.426 --> 15:29.829
WHEN YOU'RE
A MARINE PILOT.

15:29.896 --> 15:33.133
WHAT IF I DECIDE
NOT TO GO INTO THE CORPS?

15:33.200 --> 15:34.834
WELL, YOU'RE GOING IN.

15:34.901 --> 15:36.836
FOUR YEARS,
RIGHT AFTER COLLEGE.

15:36.903 --> 15:39.139
IF YOU WANT OUT
AFTER THAT, WELL,

15:39.206 --> 15:42.342
THAT'S YOUR CHOICE,
BUT YOU'RE GOING IN.

15:46.213 --> 15:49.849
WOULD YOU LIKE TO BE
KILLED IN ACTION, DAD?

15:49.916 --> 15:52.852
IT'S BETTER THAN
DYING OF PILES.

15:52.919 --> 15:54.354
YEAH.

16:07.267 --> 16:08.968
I HATE THIS PLACE.

16:09.036 --> 16:10.203
NOW, SUGAR,

16:10.270 --> 16:12.172
YOU'VE GOT TO
OPEN YOURSELF TO A TOWN.

16:12.239 --> 16:15.242
YOU'VE BEEN IN THE CORPS
LONG ENOUGH TO KNOW THAT.

16:15.308 --> 16:17.377
I AM NOT
IN THE CORPS.

16:17.444 --> 16:18.645
SAYS YOU!

16:18.711 --> 16:20.180
SHUT YOUR YAPS.

16:20.247 --> 16:23.083
THIS IS IT, SPORTS FANS...
BEAUFORT, S.C.

16:23.150 --> 16:27.087
[MARY ANNE]
TO THINK I MISTOOK IT
FOR PARIS, FRANCE.

16:31.524 --> 16:35.228
[MAN SINGING]
♪ O COME THE WILD FLOWER ♪

16:35.295 --> 16:39.332
♪ COME THE SWEET DAFFODIL ♪

16:39.399 --> 16:42.669
LOOK. LOOK AT THIS GUY.

16:42.735 --> 16:43.870
♪ COME THE GOOD HONEY ♪

16:43.936 --> 16:46.373
♪ COME
THE RIPE BERRY ♪

16:46.439 --> 16:50.610
♪ COME THE WILD FLOWER... ♪

16:52.645 --> 16:55.215
SEE IF Y'ALL
CAN GUESS WHICH HOUSE

16:55.282 --> 16:57.717
THE GREAT SANTINI HAS
RENTED FOR HIS FAMILY.

16:57.784 --> 17:01.154
SINCE THE GREAT SANTINI HAS THE
WORST TASTE IN THE FREE WORLD,

17:01.221 --> 17:02.722
IT SHOULD BE EASY.

17:02.789 --> 17:05.325
HAS THE GREAT SANTINI
EVER LET HIS FAMILY DOWN?

17:05.392 --> 17:06.925
YES!
YES!
YES!

17:06.992 --> 17:08.928
YOU DO NOT TRUST
THE GREAT SANTINI?

17:08.994 --> 17:10.329
NO!
NO!
NO!

17:10.396 --> 17:12.832
THEN HAVE A LOOK
AT THIS.

17:12.898 --> 17:14.501
WHAT?

17:16.536 --> 17:17.569
THERE.

17:19.839 --> 17:21.608
OH! OOH!

17:29.015 --> 17:31.451
OH, BULL!

17:31.518 --> 17:34.287
OH, MY GOD!

17:34.354 --> 17:36.256
CARE TO HAVE
A LOOK, SCARLETT?

17:36.323 --> 17:39.159
I'D BE CHARMED, SIR.

17:43.029 --> 17:44.264
JUST LIKE
YOU ALWAYS WANTED.

17:44.331 --> 17:47.334
I GOT A CHEAP LEASE
FROM A RICH COLONEL

17:47.400 --> 17:49.969
NAILED WITH A FAR EAST
ASSIGNMENT

17:50.036 --> 17:51.971
LOOKING
FOR A CLASSY TENANT.

17:52.038 --> 17:54.974
I PROBABLY REMINDED HIM
OF RHETT BUTLER.

17:55.041 --> 17:56.643
I'M SURE.

17:56.709 --> 17:59.279
WHAT HAVE YOU DONE?
WHAT HAVE YOU DONE?

17:59.346 --> 18:01.181
WHAT HAVE YOU...

18:02.549 --> 18:03.783
OH, MY LORD.

18:03.850 --> 18:06.286
THEY DON'T BUILD THEM
LIKE THIS ANYMORE.

18:06.353 --> 18:07.987
YOU CAN SAY THAT AGAIN.

18:08.054 --> 18:10.290
WHAT DID YOU DO?
WHAT DID YOU DO?

18:10.357 --> 18:12.492
ALL FOR YOU,
PETUNIA.

18:12.559 --> 18:16.529
OH, MY GOD. HA!

18:18.064 --> 18:20.900
YOU HAVE OUTDONE YOURSELF.

18:20.967 --> 18:23.370
GIVE US A BIG JUICY.

18:39.886 --> 18:42.455
O.K., HOGS, I'VE LISTENED
TO YOU BELLYACHE

18:42.522 --> 18:44.824
ABOUT MOVING
TO THIS NEW TOWN.

18:44.891 --> 18:48.127
THIS SAID BELLYACHING
WILL END AS OF 1530 HOURS,

18:48.195 --> 18:51.331
WILL NOT AFFECT THE MORALE
OF THIS SQUADRON HENCEFORTH.

18:51.398 --> 18:53.099
DO I MAKE MYSELF CLEAR?

18:53.166 --> 18:54.501
YES, SIR!

18:54.567 --> 18:57.337
I KNOW IT'S ROUGH
TO LEAVE YOUR FRIENDS

18:57.404 --> 18:58.805
AND MOVE EVERY YEAR,

18:58.871 --> 19:00.307
BUT YOU ARE MARINE KIDS
AND CAN CHEW NAILS

19:00.373 --> 19:04.344
WHILE OTHER KIDS
ARE SUCKING COTTON CANDY.

19:04.411 --> 19:05.845
AND YOU'RE MEECHUMS.

19:05.912 --> 19:08.881
A MEECHUM IS A THOROUGHBRED,
A WINNER ALL THE WAY,

19:08.948 --> 19:11.918
GETS THE BEST GRADES,
WINS THE MOST AWARDS,

19:11.984 --> 19:14.421
AND EXCELS IN SPORTS.

19:15.555 --> 19:17.557
A MEECHUM NEVER GIVES UP.

19:20.427 --> 19:24.063
I WANT YOU HOGS TO LET THIS BURG
KNOW YOU'RE HERE.

19:24.130 --> 19:26.366
I WANT THESE CRACKERS
TO WAKE UP

19:26.433 --> 19:28.668
AND WONDER WHAT THE HELL
BLEW INTO TOWN!

19:28.735 --> 19:32.372
O.K., HOGS, BY NIGHTFALL I WANT
THIS CAMP IN INSPECTION ORDER.

19:32.439 --> 19:34.974
DO YOU READ ME
LOUD AND CLEAR?

19:35.041 --> 19:36.276
YES, SIR!

19:36.343 --> 19:38.144
I SAID, DO YOU READ ME
LOUD AND CLEAR?

19:38.211 --> 19:40.613
[LOUDER]
YES, SIR!

19:40.680 --> 19:42.415
OUTSTANDING.

19:42.482 --> 19:44.584
SERGEANT,
DISMISS THE TROOPS.

19:55.662 --> 19:57.564
DISMISSED.

19:59.065 --> 20:01.501
HE DOES REMIND ME OF
SOMEONE FROM THE MOVIES,

20:01.568 --> 20:03.803
BUT IT'S NOT
RHETT BUTLER.

20:03.870 --> 20:04.804
WHO'S THAT?

20:04.871 --> 20:06.306
GODZILLA.

20:40.507 --> 20:42.141
COLONEL HEDGEPATH IN,
SERGEANT?

20:42.208 --> 20:43.142
NO, SIR.

20:43.209 --> 20:44.444
WHERE IS HE?

20:44.511 --> 20:45.545
HE'S INDISPOSED
AT THE MOMENT, SIR.

20:45.612 --> 20:46.946
I ASKED WHERE HE WAS,

20:47.013 --> 20:50.450
NOT FOR YOUR MASTERY
OF THE ENGLISH LANGUAGE.

20:50.517 --> 20:53.353
IN THE HEAD
DOWN THE HALL, SIR.

21:16.543 --> 21:18.678
[TOILET FLUSHES]

21:20.813 --> 21:22.749
[WHISTLING]

21:29.255 --> 21:30.690
HEY! HEY!
GODDAMN IT!

21:30.757 --> 21:31.591
GOTCHA!

21:31.658 --> 21:33.393
WHAT THE HELL?
GODDAMN IT!

21:33.460 --> 21:35.828
[SCREAMING]

21:54.080 --> 21:57.083
YOU'RE PROBABLY WONDERING
WHY I ATTACKED YOU, RIGHT?

21:57.149 --> 21:58.885
YES, SIR.

22:00.587 --> 22:02.154
WHAT'S YOUR NAME,
CORPORAL?

22:02.221 --> 22:03.556
ATCHLEY, SIR.

22:03.623 --> 22:06.526
ATCHLEY, DO YOU REALIZE
SEVERAL MARINES WERE KILLED

22:06.593 --> 22:08.528
BY THE JAPANESE
AT PEARL HARBOR

22:08.595 --> 22:10.096
WHILE TAKING CRAPS?

22:10.162 --> 22:11.531
NO, SIR.

22:11.598 --> 22:14.033
A FIGHTING MAN MUST BE
VIGILANT TO SURPRISE ATTACK

22:14.100 --> 22:15.334
NO MATTER WHERE HE IS.

22:15.402 --> 22:16.769
THE SURVIVAL
OF OUR NATION

22:16.836 --> 22:20.707
DEPENDS ON THE READINESS
OF MARINES ALL OVER THE WORLD.

22:20.773 --> 22:24.010
ALSO, AND MORE IMPORTANT,
YOU ONLY WIPED YOURSELF TWICE.

22:25.512 --> 22:27.414
GROSSLY INSUFFICIENT.

22:27.480 --> 22:29.849
RIGHT NOW, GERMS WITH NAMES
YOU CAN'T EVEN PRONOUNCE

22:29.916 --> 22:31.984
ARE PREPARING TO LAUNCH
A DEVASTATING ATTACK

22:32.051 --> 22:34.954
THAT WILL RENDER YOU HELPLESS
IN DEFENDING YOUR COUNTRY.

22:35.021 --> 22:35.722
DO YOU READ ME?

22:35.788 --> 22:38.290
YES, SIR.

22:38.357 --> 22:40.259
GOOD. I'M COLONEL
JOHN J. JONES.

22:40.326 --> 22:42.562
I'M ONLY HERE
FOR THE DAY.

22:42.629 --> 22:45.565
I FLY AROUND THE COUNTRY
TESTING THE READINESS OF TROOPS.

22:45.632 --> 22:48.568
THIS IS A STRICTLY
CONFIDENTIAL TEST,

22:48.635 --> 22:51.303
CLASSIFIED TOP SECRET.

22:51.370 --> 22:54.941
TELL NO ONE, ATCHLEY,

22:55.007 --> 22:57.577
AND IF YOU EVER ATTACK
A SENIOR OFFICER AGAIN,

22:57.644 --> 22:58.878
I'LL HAVE YOU
COURT-MARTIALED.

22:58.945 --> 23:00.613
BUT YOU ATTACKED
ME, SIR.

23:00.680 --> 23:04.183
DISMISSED! GOOD LUCK
IN YOUR CAREER.

23:04.250 --> 23:05.418
BE PROUD, ATCHLEY...

23:05.485 --> 23:07.954
PROUD OF YOURSELF
AND PROUD OF THE CORPS.

23:08.020 --> 23:09.288
NOW GET OUT.

23:09.355 --> 23:10.823
YES, SIR.

23:14.293 --> 23:16.128
[SIGH]

23:17.664 --> 23:19.599
YOU SILVER-TONGUED BASTARD.

23:19.666 --> 23:21.834
SHAME ON YOU.

23:24.370 --> 23:25.572
IS HE BACK YET, COP?

23:25.638 --> 23:28.508
YES, SIR.
HE'S EXPECTING YOU.

23:32.879 --> 23:34.046
BANZAI!

23:34.113 --> 23:36.716
AAH!

23:36.783 --> 23:37.950
CLOSE THAT DOOR,
SERGEANT!

23:38.017 --> 23:40.419
I DON'T WANT TO
HUMILIATE THIS MAN

23:40.487 --> 23:43.656
ANY MORE THAN I HAVE TO.

23:43.723 --> 23:45.625
NOW, COLONEL,
REPEAT AFTER ME...

23:45.692 --> 23:47.627
BULL MEECHUM
HAS MENSTRUAL CRAMPS.

23:47.694 --> 23:50.630
KISS ME WHERE
THE SKIN TURNS PINK,

23:50.697 --> 23:52.632
YOU WORTHLESS SCUM!

23:52.699 --> 23:54.433
WHAT KIND OF MAN
ASSAULTS CORPORALS

23:54.501 --> 23:55.702
WITH THEIR PANTS DOWN?

23:55.768 --> 23:57.003
I WANT TO KNOW
ABOUT THAT ONE.

23:57.069 --> 23:59.472
AAH! AAH! AAH!

23:59.539 --> 24:03.543
[LAUGHING]

24:08.715 --> 24:10.316
HOW ARE YOU, VIRG?

24:10.382 --> 24:11.350
I'M GOOD.

24:11.417 --> 24:13.352
GOOD TO SEE YOU,
BUDDY.

24:13.419 --> 24:15.021
WHOO!

24:15.087 --> 24:18.424
AHH, WELCOME ABOARD, BULL.

24:18.491 --> 24:20.092
TELL ME WHO PUT ME
IN VARNEY'S GROUP.

24:20.159 --> 24:21.227
HE HATES MY GUTS.

24:21.293 --> 24:22.662
I KNOW. I KNOW.

24:22.729 --> 24:24.363
THE SQUADRON'S
IN TROUBLE.

24:24.430 --> 24:25.732
USED TO BE
ONE OF THE BEST,

24:25.798 --> 24:28.601
BUT THE LAST TWO C.O.s
REALLY LET IT SLIP.

24:28.668 --> 24:30.770
VARNEY'S IN LINE
FOR A STAR, YOU KNOW.

24:30.837 --> 24:32.672
HE KNOWS IF HE'S GOING
TO MAKE GENERAL,

24:32.739 --> 24:34.674
HE'LL HAVE TO
SHAPE UP THE 312th.

24:34.741 --> 24:36.809
IT'S THAT SIMPLE.

24:38.511 --> 24:41.380
YOU HEARD
I GOT PASSED OVER?

24:41.447 --> 24:43.516
PASSED OVER?

24:43.583 --> 24:45.384
YOU'RE LUCKY
YOU DIDN'T GET BUSTED.

24:45.451 --> 24:48.120
I HEARD ABOUT
THAT MUSHROOM SOUP STUNT.

24:48.187 --> 24:49.221
YEAH?

24:49.288 --> 24:50.322
YEAH.

24:50.389 --> 24:51.691
GO AHEAD AND GRIN,
DUMMY.

24:51.758 --> 24:53.392
I'M TELLING YOU,
BULL,

24:53.459 --> 24:55.728
YOU BETTER WATCH
YOUR SIX FROM NOW ON.

24:55.795 --> 24:57.930
YOU'VE GOT
YOUR SQUADRON, RIGHT?

24:57.997 --> 25:00.232
JUST KEEP YOUR NOSE
CLEAN FOR A CHANGE.

25:00.299 --> 25:01.801
YES, SIR.

25:01.868 --> 25:05.204
AND DON'T GO RAPING ANY MORE
CORPORALS IN THE LATRINE,

25:05.271 --> 25:07.173
COLONEL JONES.

25:07.239 --> 25:08.541
YES, YES.

25:08.608 --> 25:11.277
MY GOD,
YOU NEVER CHANGE.

25:12.478 --> 25:15.615
[JET TAKES OFF]

25:23.990 --> 25:26.926
WHAT ARE YOU
THINKING, COLONEL?

25:26.993 --> 25:28.661
NOTHING, SIR.

25:30.797 --> 25:32.531
YES, YOU ARE,
WILBUR.

25:32.599 --> 25:35.134
YOU'RE THINKING, "WHY
DOESN'T THAT SON OF A BITCH

25:35.201 --> 25:36.736
"QUIT READING
THOSE DAMN PAPERS

25:36.803 --> 25:38.605
AND WELCOME ME ABOARD
THIS STATION?"

25:38.671 --> 25:40.740
ISN'T THAT WHAT
YOU WERE THINKING?

25:40.807 --> 25:42.942
YES, SIR. THAT'S EXACTLY
WHAT I WAS THINKING, SIR.

25:43.009 --> 25:44.543
SIT DOWN.

25:48.648 --> 25:50.950
O.K., NOW UNDERSTAND
THIS, WILBUR.

25:51.017 --> 25:53.352
THE ONLY REASON I PICKED
YOU FOR THIS JOB...

25:53.419 --> 25:54.787
DESPITE THE FACT

25:54.854 --> 25:57.590
THAT YOU'RE A
DISGRACE TO THE CORPS

25:57.657 --> 25:59.558
AND ON YOUR WAY TO
BEING AN ALCOHOLIC...

25:59.626 --> 26:02.328
IS THAT YOU'RE A FAIR LEADER
AND A CRACKERJACK PILOT.

26:02.394 --> 26:03.429
THANK YOU, SIR.

26:03.495 --> 26:07.299
JUST SIT THERE
AND SHUT UP.

26:07.366 --> 26:10.269
CUBA IS HOT.
VERY HOT.

26:10.336 --> 26:13.272
IF IT POPS, WE'LL BE RIGHT
IN THE MIDDLE OF IT.

26:13.339 --> 26:16.809
NOW, I WANT YOU TO START GETTING
THESE PILOTS INTO SHAPE.

26:16.876 --> 26:18.611
AS MUCH AS I NEED
THIS JOB DONE,

26:18.678 --> 26:22.481
IT WON'T BREAK MY HEART IF
YOU FALL ON YOUR BUTT AGAIN.

26:22.548 --> 26:23.916
THAT WAY I CAN END
YOUR CAREER

26:23.983 --> 26:26.152
WITH A POOR
FITNESS REPORT.

26:26.218 --> 26:27.486
DO YOU READ ME?

26:27.553 --> 26:29.255
YES, SIR.

26:29.321 --> 26:31.123
THAT'S ALL.

26:34.694 --> 26:36.696
DISMISSED.

26:38.364 --> 26:40.466
GET YOUR TROUSERS
PRESSED, COLONEL.

26:40.532 --> 26:42.601
YES, SIR.

26:42.669 --> 26:44.136
[BULL IMITATING BUGLE]

26:44.203 --> 26:45.972
♪ IT'S TIME TO GET UP
IN THE MORNING ♪

26:46.038 --> 26:47.774
RISE AND SHINE,
SPLIT TAILS!

26:47.840 --> 26:49.776
INSPECTION AT 0900
BY COMMANDING OFFICER.

26:49.842 --> 26:52.478
0900! LILLIAN!

26:52.544 --> 26:54.446
I'M HUNGRY!
RISE AND SHINE!

26:54.513 --> 26:55.147
DAD!

26:55.214 --> 26:56.415
JESUS!

26:56.482 --> 26:59.819
HEY, LILLIAN, THE LITTLE HOMO'S
SLEEPING NAKED!

26:59.886 --> 27:01.620
LET'S GO! UP AND OUT!

27:02.955 --> 27:05.424
LET'S SHAKE IT OUT, HOG.
INSPECTION AT 0900.

27:05.491 --> 27:08.160
LET'S GO!

27:21.941 --> 27:24.043
STAND BY FOR
A FIGHTER PILOT.

27:24.110 --> 27:25.912
WHAT YOU SAY,
CAPTAIN?

27:25.978 --> 27:28.948
I AM THE GREAT SANTINI!

27:29.015 --> 27:32.852
I'S ARRABELLE SMALLS,
YOUR NEW MAID.

27:32.919 --> 27:35.087
NEVER WORKED FOR
NO ITALIAN BEFORE.

27:35.154 --> 27:36.723
PURE IRISH.

27:36.789 --> 27:38.858
MADAM, YOU'RE
A SOLID-LOOKING WOMAN.

27:38.925 --> 27:40.860
I CAN PUNCH
HARD AS A MAN.

27:40.927 --> 27:42.094
YOU WANT TO HIT
MY SHOULDER?

27:42.161 --> 27:43.162
THIS IS A MARINE
YOU'RE TALKING TO.

27:43.229 --> 27:45.765
I MIGHT CAUSE
INTERNAL BLEEDING.

27:45.832 --> 27:47.166
SHOOT, MAN.

27:47.233 --> 27:48.901
YOU GO ON AND HIT
ARRABELLE'S SHOULDER.

27:48.968 --> 27:51.370
COME ON DOWN HERE.

27:54.741 --> 27:58.878
O.K., LADY, WATCH OUT.

28:00.747 --> 28:02.915
YOU ARE SOLID AS A ROCK.

28:02.982 --> 28:04.683
NOW IT'S MY TURN.

28:04.751 --> 28:06.318
RIGHT HERE. GO ON.

28:09.856 --> 28:11.390
OHH, GOD! WHOA!

28:11.457 --> 28:13.192
WAIT! YOU CALL
THAT PUNCHING?

28:13.259 --> 28:15.161
YOU WANT ME
TO DO IT AGAIN?

28:15.227 --> 28:16.528
HELL, NO.
IF YOU HURT YOUR HAND,

28:16.595 --> 28:18.898
I'LL HAVE TO PAY
THE DOCTOR BILLS.

28:18.965 --> 28:21.200
WHAT IS GOING ON
OUT HERE?

28:21.267 --> 28:23.402
OH! WHY, YOU MUST BE
MRS. SMALLS.

28:23.469 --> 28:24.436
I IS.

28:24.503 --> 28:25.938
I'M LILLIAN MEECHUM,

28:26.005 --> 28:28.640
AND THIS IS MY HUSBAND
LIEUTENANT COLONEL BULL MEECHUM.

28:28.707 --> 28:30.476
MY KIND OF WOMAN.

28:30.542 --> 28:32.711
OH, YEAH?
THAT SAYS A LOT.

28:32.779 --> 28:34.713
ERLINE GRANTHAM
SPOKE VERY HIGHLY OF YOU.

28:34.781 --> 28:36.783
SHE SAID YOU SPENT
A LOT OF TIME IN JAIL

28:36.849 --> 28:39.485
FOR STEALING SILVER
OUT OF NICE HOUSES.

28:39.551 --> 28:42.521
MISS ERLINE DON'T PUT NO
TRASH MOUTH ON ME, CAPTAIN.

28:42.588 --> 28:44.857
YOU'LL GET USED TO
HIS TEASING OR YOU WON'T.

28:44.924 --> 28:47.726
IT'LL BE THERE
ONE WAY OR THE OTHER.

28:47.794 --> 28:50.729
LILLIAN, I WANT CHOW.
IT IS I, SANTINI!

28:50.797 --> 28:53.732
BEAST OF BEAUFORT
WANTS HIS BREAKFAST!

28:53.800 --> 28:55.434
EAT!

28:55.501 --> 28:56.735
EAT!

28:56.803 --> 28:58.237
WELL, I HOPE
YOU LIKE CHILDREN.

28:58.304 --> 28:59.839
WE HAVE FOUR.

28:59.906 --> 29:03.275
CHILDREN IS THE ONLY
PERFECT PEOPLE THERE IS.

29:03.342 --> 29:04.376
I GOT ME A FINE BOY.

29:04.443 --> 29:07.013
HE SELLS HONEY AND
FLOWERS HEREABOUTS.

29:07.079 --> 29:09.048
IS HE THE ONE THAT DRIVES
A WAGON AND MULE?

29:09.115 --> 29:11.683
THAT'S HIM.
THAT'S MY BOY TOOMER.

29:11.750 --> 29:13.385
[BULL]
CASTRO, YOU BEARDED FAG!

29:13.452 --> 29:17.123
I'D LIKE TO CHASE YOU DOWN THE
MAIN STREET OF HAVANA IN MY F-4!

29:17.189 --> 29:18.557
AND DE GAULLE!

29:18.624 --> 29:22.461
GOD, WHY DO YOU PUT SO
MANY JERKS IN THE WORLD

29:22.528 --> 29:23.863
AT THE SAME TIME?

29:23.930 --> 29:25.264
KIND OF PECULIAR,
AIN'T HE?

29:25.331 --> 29:29.768
HE'S JUST READING
HIS PAPER. COME ON IN.

29:29.836 --> 29:31.470
ATTENTION ON DECK.

29:33.039 --> 29:34.974
SEATS, GENTLEMEN.

29:38.811 --> 29:40.346
MORNING.
YOU MEN HAVE THE PRIVILEGE

29:40.412 --> 29:42.114
OF SERVING UNDER THE MEANEST,
TOUGHEST, SCREAMINGEST

29:42.181 --> 29:46.052
SQUADRON COMMANDER
IN THE MARINE CORPS... ME.

29:46.118 --> 29:48.754
NOW, I DON'T WANT YOU
TO CONSIDER ME

29:48.821 --> 29:51.023
AS JUST
YOUR COMMANDING OFFICER.

29:51.090 --> 29:54.793
I WANT YOU TO LOOK ON ME
LIKE I WAS...

29:54.861 --> 29:57.496
WELL...

29:58.865 --> 30:00.967
GOD.

30:01.033 --> 30:03.903
IF I SAY SOMETHING,

30:03.970 --> 30:06.005
YOU PRETEND IT'S COMING
FROM THE BURNING BUSH.

30:06.072 --> 30:07.373
NOW, WE'RE MEMBERS
OF THE PROUDEST,

30:07.439 --> 30:11.210
MOST ELITE GROUP
OF FIGHTING MEN IN THE WORLD.

30:11.277 --> 30:13.512
WE ARE MARINE CORPS
FIGHTER PILOTS.

30:13.579 --> 30:16.015
WE HAVE NO OTHER FUNCTION.

30:16.082 --> 30:18.985
THAT IS OUR MISSION,

30:19.051 --> 30:21.553
AND YOU'RE EITHER
GOING TO HACK IT...

30:21.620 --> 30:22.955
OR PACK IT.

30:23.022 --> 30:24.290
DO YOU READ ME?

30:24.356 --> 30:25.992
WITHIN 30 DAYS,
I'M GOING TO LEAD

30:26.058 --> 30:28.427
THE TOUGHEST, FLYINGEST
SONS OF BITCHES IN THE WORLD.

30:28.494 --> 30:32.031
THE 312 WEREWOLF SQUADRON
WILL MAKE HISTORY,

30:32.098 --> 30:35.601
OR IT WILL DIE TRYING.

30:35.667 --> 30:37.369
NOW, YOU'RE FLYING
WITH BULL MEECHUM NOW,

30:37.436 --> 30:42.541
AND I KID YOU NOT...
THIS IS THE EYE OF THE STORM.

30:42.608 --> 30:44.143
WELCOME ABOARD.

30:46.445 --> 30:48.981
CARRY ON.

30:49.048 --> 30:51.050
[MURMURING]

30:54.753 --> 30:56.555
COME ON! HEY, HEY, HEY!

30:56.622 --> 30:58.224
HEY, HEY, HEY!

30:58.290 --> 31:00.759
[CHEERING]

31:00.826 --> 31:02.694
O.K., BENNY BOY!

31:02.761 --> 31:05.097
COME ON, NOW.

31:06.032 --> 31:07.466
DAD, DAD, DAD!

31:07.533 --> 31:09.301
DAD, DAD, DAD!

31:09.368 --> 31:10.502
COME ON, NOW.

31:10.569 --> 31:12.204
THE REASON I'M GOING
TO BEAT YOU, DAD,

31:12.271 --> 31:15.274
IS BECAUSE YOU'RE
GETTING A LITTLE FAT.

31:17.543 --> 31:19.245
YEAH? YEAH?

31:21.380 --> 31:24.083
ONE. THAT'S ONE.

31:28.654 --> 31:29.721
OHH!

31:29.788 --> 31:31.023
HOW ABOUT THAT,
SPORTS FANS?

31:31.090 --> 31:34.260
[CHEERING]

31:34.326 --> 31:37.629
WE KNOW
YOU CAN DO THAT.

31:41.968 --> 31:44.603
GO, BENNY BOY!

31:45.637 --> 31:47.073
HEY, HEY, FOUL!

31:47.139 --> 31:49.008
FOUL. HE'S STARTING
TO CHEAT.

31:49.075 --> 31:50.943
2-1. NO FOUL.

31:51.010 --> 31:52.644
DID YOU SEE THAT?

31:52.711 --> 31:55.347
2-1. 2-1. 2-1.
NO FOUL.

31:55.414 --> 31:57.449
NO FOUL. 2-1.

32:00.987 --> 32:01.787
WHO'S FOR ME?
WHO'S FOR ME?

32:01.853 --> 32:03.555
LET'S HEAR IT!

32:03.622 --> 32:05.257
STAY IN THERE.

32:06.558 --> 32:08.760
OW!

32:08.827 --> 32:09.895
THAT'S DIRTY PLAY.

32:09.962 --> 32:12.931
8-6, HOG.
YOU'RE FINISHED.

32:12.999 --> 32:15.134
SAYS YOU.

32:19.905 --> 32:22.941
HOW DO YOU FEEL, DAD?

32:23.009 --> 32:24.610
YOU LOOK A LITTLE TIRED.

32:24.676 --> 32:26.645
LOOK A LITTLE RAGGED.

32:33.719 --> 32:35.554
GEE!

32:35.621 --> 32:36.622
HEY! HA HA!

32:36.688 --> 32:38.957
9-9.
DON'T WORRY, COLONEL,

32:39.025 --> 32:41.560
YOU CAN ALWAYS GET
A DISABILITY PENSION.

32:41.627 --> 32:43.062
DON'T GOAD HIM, BEN.

32:43.129 --> 32:44.730
COME ON, JUST PLAY.

32:44.796 --> 32:47.699
LAST SHOT, JOCKO.
GIVE UP?

32:47.766 --> 32:50.102
STAY CLOSE, BEN.
NOW, WATCH HIM.

32:52.204 --> 32:54.106
WHIP HIS FANNY, BEN!

32:54.173 --> 32:58.077
IT IS I,
THE GREAT BENTINI!

32:58.144 --> 32:59.545
DO YOU KNOW, DAD,

32:59.611 --> 33:02.114
NOT ONE OF US HAS EVER
BEATEN YOU AT A SINGLE GAME?

33:02.181 --> 33:06.552
NOT CHECKERS, NOT
DOMINOES, NOT SOFTBALL.

33:06.618 --> 33:09.055
WATCH IT, BEN.
HE'S GETTING THAT LOOK.

33:09.121 --> 33:11.390
COME OVER HERE. COME
OVER HERE TO DADDY BULL.

33:11.457 --> 33:13.625
IT'S ALL OVER,
COLONEL.

33:16.628 --> 33:18.397
[CHEERING]

33:18.464 --> 33:19.998
YOU PLAYED
A GREAT GAME, DAD.

33:20.066 --> 33:22.668
GET OUT OF HERE BEFORE I KNOCK
EVERY FRECKLE OFF YOUR FACE.

33:22.734 --> 33:25.504
THAT'S MEAN.

33:25.571 --> 33:26.705
WASN'T THAT GREAT?

33:26.772 --> 33:28.840
COME ON, JOCKO. YOU GOT
TO WIN BY TWO BASKETS.

33:28.907 --> 33:29.975
YOU SAID ONE.

33:30.042 --> 33:32.211
I CHANGED MY MIND.
LET'S GO.

33:32.278 --> 33:34.413
DON'T CHEAT THE BOY
OUT OF HIS VICTORY.

33:34.480 --> 33:37.516
WHO THE HELL
ASKED YOU ANYTHING?

33:37.583 --> 33:39.017
DON'T YOU TALK
TO ME LIKE THAT!

33:39.085 --> 33:40.419
I'LL PLAY HIM, MOM.

33:40.486 --> 33:43.389
NO. HE BEAT YOU, AND
IT WAS BEAUTIFUL.

33:43.455 --> 33:45.857
YOU BETTER GET IN THE HOUSE
BEFORE I KICK YOUR BUTT.

33:45.924 --> 33:46.992
NOW, I MEAN IT.
COME ON.

33:47.059 --> 33:49.295
LET'S GO. HURRY.
COME ON.

33:49.361 --> 33:51.029
YOU BETTER MOVE,
WOMAN.

33:51.097 --> 33:52.731
ALL RIGHT!

33:54.833 --> 33:55.901
COME ON. LET'S GO.

33:55.967 --> 33:58.537
HE BEAT YOU.

33:58.604 --> 33:59.605
GET OUT OF HERE!

34:00.506 --> 34:02.441
KIND OF LIKE
WINNING, HUH, DAD?

34:02.508 --> 34:05.177
GET SMART WITH ME,
I'LL KICK YOUR BUTT.

34:05.244 --> 34:06.178
GUARD ME. YOU GOT
TO WIN BY TWO.

34:06.245 --> 34:08.179
I'M NOT GOING TO.
I WON.

34:08.246 --> 34:11.217
MAMMA'S BOY, I BET
YOU'RE GOING TO CRY.

34:11.283 --> 34:15.053
COME ON, MAMMA'S BOY.
LET'S SEE YOU CRY.

34:15.121 --> 34:17.054
SQUIRT A FEW.
COME ON, CRY.

34:17.123 --> 34:18.889
COME ON, CRY.

34:18.956 --> 34:21.127
COME ON! JUST A FEW.
COME ON.

34:21.193 --> 34:24.763
SQUIRT A FEW. COME ON.

34:24.830 --> 34:25.897
COME ON, CRY.

34:25.964 --> 34:29.635
1, 2, 3, CRY.
1, 2, 3, CRY.

34:29.701 --> 34:33.539
COME ON! CRY.

34:33.605 --> 34:34.440
COME ON, BABY.

34:34.505 --> 34:37.042
COME ON,
LITTLE GIRL, CRY.

34:37.109 --> 34:38.444
CRY.

34:39.445 --> 34:40.746
YOU'RE MY FAVORITE
DAUGHTER, BEN.

34:40.812 --> 34:43.815
I SWEAR TO GOD YOU'RE
MY SWEETEST LITTLE GIRL.

34:43.882 --> 34:47.786
THIS LITTLE GIRL JUST WHIPPED
YOUR ASS GOOD, COLONEL!

34:51.257 --> 34:53.292
[BASKETBALL BOUNCING]

35:41.440 --> 35:43.742
HOW ARE YOU
FEELING, SUGAR?

35:44.610 --> 35:47.145
I'M O.K., MAMMA.

35:47.213 --> 35:49.348
HOW ARE YOU?

35:50.849 --> 35:53.852
OH, I'LL LIVE
THROUGH THE NIGHT.

35:59.458 --> 36:01.560
YOU KNOW WHAT
I WAS THINKING?

36:01.627 --> 36:03.362
WHAT?

36:09.368 --> 36:13.038
I WAS PRAYING WE'D
ALL GO TO WAR AGAIN

36:13.104 --> 36:14.540
SO KING KONG OUT THERE

36:14.606 --> 36:17.843
COULD FIGHT SOMEBODY
BESIDES ME.

36:17.909 --> 36:22.681
SHAME ON YOU. THAT'S
A TERRIBLE THING TO SAY.

36:22.748 --> 36:25.384
YOUR FATHER LOVES YOU
VERY MUCH.

36:25.451 --> 36:27.653
HE'S GOT A FABULOUS WAY
OF SHOWING IT, MA.

36:27.719 --> 36:29.054
YOU'RE GOING TO
CUT OFF

36:29.120 --> 36:33.559
ALL YOUR CIRCULATION
DOING THAT.

36:43.001 --> 36:45.904
DO YOU LOVE HIM?

36:47.373 --> 36:49.207
OF COURSE.

36:49.275 --> 36:51.310
OF COURSE I DO.

36:51.377 --> 36:55.981
I THINK HE TREATS
YOU CRAPPY.

36:56.047 --> 37:01.253
OH, HARSH WORDS WERE
NEVER FATAL TO ANYBODY.

37:01.320 --> 37:05.924
WELL, WHAT ABOUT
HARSH KICKS, MAMMA?

37:05.991 --> 37:07.058
HE WAS GETTING READY...

37:07.125 --> 37:09.227
WELL, HE DIDN'T.

37:09.295 --> 37:11.497
BEN, YOUR FATHER HAS
NEVER HIT ME ONCE

37:11.563 --> 37:14.232
DURING OUR ENTIRE
MARRIED LIFE.

37:14.300 --> 37:15.934
[SIGH]

37:16.001 --> 37:17.202
OH, HONEY.

37:17.269 --> 37:18.470
WHAT HAPPENED TODAY

37:18.537 --> 37:21.373
WON'T MAKE ANY DIFFERENCE
IN FIVE YEARS.

37:21.440 --> 37:24.242
HE DOES WHAT HE DOES
BECAUSE HE LOVES YOU,

37:24.310 --> 37:26.678
AND HE WANTS YOU
TO BE THE BEST.

37:26.745 --> 37:28.780
OH, SURE.

37:28.847 --> 37:30.882
"I LOVE YOU, BEN."

37:30.949 --> 37:32.818
PUNCH.

37:32.884 --> 37:35.153
"I WANT YOU TO BE
THE BEST, BEN."

37:35.220 --> 37:36.522
KICK.

37:36.588 --> 37:39.725
"AND, BEN, I THINK
YOU'RE GREAT, BEN."

37:39.791 --> 37:42.694
BOUNCE THE BASKETBALL
OFF OF MY HEAD.

37:42.761 --> 37:46.097
OH, STOP IT. HASN'T
THERE BEEN ENOUGH?

37:46.164 --> 37:48.133
COME OVER HERE.

37:48.199 --> 37:49.768
YOU KNOW WHY
HE'S DOWN THERE?

37:49.835 --> 37:51.169
NO, MA'AM.

37:51.236 --> 37:53.138
WELL, I'LL TELL YOU.

37:53.204 --> 37:55.273
HE IS ADMITTING
TO YOU

37:55.341 --> 37:57.275
THAT THE GAP
IS CLOSING,

37:57.343 --> 37:58.577
THAT HE'S GOING TO
HAVE TO PRACTICE

37:58.644 --> 38:02.047
IF HE BEATS YOU
FROM NOW ON.

38:02.113 --> 38:05.351
HE'S ADMITTING TO YOU
THAT HE'S GETTING OLDER,

38:05.417 --> 38:06.852
AND THAT IS THE HARDEST
THING IN THE WORLD

38:06.918 --> 38:08.019
FOR A MAN LIKE BULL.

38:08.086 --> 38:10.756
WELL, MAMMA, THAT DOESN'T
CHANGE ANYTHING.

38:10.822 --> 38:13.091
WELL, IT SHOULD.

38:13.158 --> 38:18.196
DON'T YOU THINK HE KNOWS THAT
YOU'RE UP HERE WATCHING HIM?

38:18.263 --> 38:22.334
YOU'VE GOT
A STRANGE FATHER, BEN.

38:28.374 --> 38:30.108
WELL, THAT'S THE ONLY WAY
HE KNOWS HOW TO SAY,

38:30.175 --> 38:33.211
"I'M SORRY, SON."

38:33.278 --> 38:34.680
AND LET ME TELL YOU,

38:34.746 --> 38:37.282
THERE ISN'T ANOTHER PERSON
IN GOD'S GOOD WORLD

38:37.349 --> 38:38.750
THAT HE WOULD DO THAT FOR.

38:38.817 --> 38:42.053
HA HA HA.

38:42.120 --> 38:46.825
YOU TRY TO THINK OF THAT WHEN
YOU FEEL HE DOESN'T LOVE YOU.

38:46.892 --> 38:48.527
HUH.

38:49.795 --> 38:52.063
GET OUT OF
THOSE CLOTHES, HUH?

38:52.130 --> 38:54.332
TAKE A SHOWER.

38:54.400 --> 38:57.002
DO YOU WANT
ANYTHING TO EAT?

38:57.068 --> 39:00.772
SURE?

39:00.839 --> 39:03.542
I LOVE YOU.

39:12.117 --> 39:14.052
[BASKETBALL BOUNCING]

39:30.268 --> 39:33.371
[BULL]
O.K, CLOSE IT UP.
I WANT YOU RIGHT UP HIS SIX.

39:33.439 --> 39:35.373
STAY ON HIM.
STAY ON HIM, WIZARD.

39:35.441 --> 39:39.611
CLOSE! CLOSE!

39:39.678 --> 39:42.380
LEFT, MILKMAN, LEFT.

39:42.448 --> 39:45.350
NOW TURN. TURN!

39:45.417 --> 39:47.719
NO, NO. ANTICIPATE.

39:47.786 --> 39:50.088
SEE THAT BOGY,
WIZARD.

39:50.155 --> 39:51.690
BLEED HIM, BLEED HIM.

39:51.757 --> 39:53.592
O.K., YOU'RE LINED UP.

39:53.659 --> 39:55.994
HE'S ON YOU, MILKMAN.
DO SOMETHING.

39:56.061 --> 39:58.196
COME LEFT. TIGHTER.

39:58.263 --> 40:00.198
TIGHTER, WIZARD.

40:00.265 --> 40:02.434
PRESS HIM. PUSH HIM!

40:02.501 --> 40:04.603
THERE'S A SHOT. THERE IT IS.

40:04.670 --> 40:06.505
IT'S ALL OVER, MILKMAN.
BANG.

40:06.572 --> 40:08.406
THAT'S A KILL.

40:09.875 --> 40:12.343
GO LAY DOWN AND DIE, MILKMAN.
YOU'RE FINISHED.

40:12.410 --> 40:13.912
THAT'S A KILL.

40:13.979 --> 40:15.847
WHAT ARE YOU BOYS
DOING DOWN THERE?

40:15.914 --> 40:18.016
TAKE HIM INTO THE SUN,
BARSTOOL.

40:18.083 --> 40:20.185
UP, UP. THAT'S IT.
WATCH YOUR SIX.

40:20.251 --> 40:22.588
WATCH YOUR SIX!

40:23.555 --> 40:25.323
WHAT THE HELL? WATCH...

40:25.390 --> 40:27.459
WATCH...

40:27.526 --> 40:30.295
WHAT'S THE MATTER
WITH YOU GUYS?

40:30.361 --> 40:31.497
KILL THE BOGY,
NOT YOUR LEADER.

40:31.563 --> 40:32.964
YOU FLY
LIKE A BUNCH OF PUSSIES!

40:33.031 --> 40:36.134
JESUS CHRIST!

40:47.613 --> 40:49.648
[ARF ARF]

40:52.150 --> 40:53.752
[ARF ARF]

40:53.819 --> 40:55.253
HUSH.

40:55.320 --> 40:56.287
HUSH UP.

40:56.354 --> 40:57.989
[MULE BRAYING]

40:58.056 --> 41:01.793
THAT'S ABOUT THE UGLIEST
CAT I EVER DID SEE.

41:05.664 --> 41:08.266
THAT'S THE UGLIEST
LOOKING COW

41:08.333 --> 41:11.803
PULLING THAT WAGON
I EVER DID SEE.

41:11.870 --> 41:15.641
A COW! WHY, THIS
HERE IS MAN O' WAR,

41:15.707 --> 41:19.578
WINNER OF
THE KENTUCKY DERBY.

41:19.645 --> 41:22.280
THAT THERE
IS RIN TIN TIN,

41:22.347 --> 41:24.583
STAR OF STAGE,
SCREEN, AND TV.

41:24.650 --> 41:26.184
HEY, TOOMER.

41:26.251 --> 41:27.586
HI, MAMMA.

41:27.653 --> 41:29.588
MRS. MEECHUM, THIS
HERE'S MY SON TOOMER.

41:29.655 --> 41:31.590
WHY, TOOMER,
IT IS A PLEASURE.

41:31.657 --> 41:33.291
HOW ARE YOU,
MA'AM?

41:33.358 --> 41:34.425
FINE.

41:34.492 --> 41:36.161
THESE HERE
ARE FOR YOU.

41:36.227 --> 41:39.464
WHY, HOW LOVELY.
BLESS YOUR HEART.

41:39.531 --> 41:40.699
WELL, WHERE
YOU HEADING, SON?

41:40.766 --> 41:43.602
I THOUGHT I'D DO ME
SOME F-F-FISHING.

41:43.669 --> 41:45.537
YOU BRING ME BACK
SOME NICE FLOUNDER

41:45.604 --> 41:48.306
SO I CAN FIX
FOR THIS FAMILY.

41:48.373 --> 41:49.608
YOU DONE
MUCH FISHING, BEN?

41:49.675 --> 41:51.309
NOT IN SALT WATER.

41:51.376 --> 41:52.644
WELL, WHY
DON'T YOU GO?

41:52.711 --> 41:56.181
YOU WANT TO COME ALONG,
DRIBBLING MAN?

41:56.247 --> 41:57.448
WE BE OUT ALL NIGHT.

41:57.515 --> 41:58.183
COULD I, MOM?

41:58.249 --> 41:59.417
WELL, SURE.

41:59.484 --> 42:01.352
GET YOUR JACKET
AND SOME BLANKETS.

42:01.419 --> 42:03.454
RIGHT WITH YOU.

42:03.521 --> 42:07.125
THAT POOR BOY HAS LIVED IN
CITIES AND ON BASES SO LONG,

42:07.192 --> 42:09.260
HE'S NEVER REALLY
TASTED THE SOUTH.

42:09.327 --> 42:11.129
OH, THANK YOU,
TOOMER.

42:11.196 --> 42:14.265
I'M GOING TO FIX YOU SOME SWEET
POTATO PIE THIS WEEKEND.

42:14.332 --> 42:15.801
THANK YOU.

42:15.867 --> 42:18.536
THANK YOU
FOR THESE. BYE.

42:18.604 --> 42:20.238
SEE YOU, MAMMA.

42:20.305 --> 42:21.840
BYE.

42:25.711 --> 42:27.345
LOOK COMING HERE.

42:27.412 --> 42:29.815
[LAUGHING]

42:30.716 --> 42:33.652
HEY, T-T-TOOMER.

42:33.719 --> 42:38.657
HOW YOU D-D-DOING,
B-B-BOSS?

42:38.724 --> 42:40.659
WHO WAS THAT?

42:40.726 --> 42:43.662
HE AIN'T NOBODY.

42:43.729 --> 42:45.664
NAME'S RED PETTUS.

42:45.731 --> 42:48.667
HIM AND HIS FAMILY
H-H-HATE A BLACK MAN

42:48.734 --> 42:52.370
J-J-JUST
FOR BEING BLACK.

42:52.437 --> 42:54.673
THEY'S SHRIMP FOLK.

42:54.740 --> 42:59.978
OLD RED... CAN'T
EVEN TALK TO HIM.

43:42.788 --> 43:44.622
[DOGS BARKING]

43:47.693 --> 43:51.730
WOW. HOW MANY DOGS
YOU GOT HERE?

43:51.797 --> 43:53.932
DON'T RIGHTLY KNOW.

43:53.999 --> 43:55.801
12, 14.

43:55.867 --> 43:58.704
MAYBE MORE. SOME
COMES AND GOES.

43:58.770 --> 44:00.739
IS THAT
WHERE YOU LIVE?

44:00.806 --> 44:04.142
HOME SWEET HOME.
WHOA, WHOA.

44:06.177 --> 44:08.747
YOU GOT TO MAKE FRIENDS
WITH THE GRAY.

44:08.814 --> 44:10.648
WHO'S THE GRAY?

44:11.817 --> 44:13.451
SEE HIM?

44:13.518 --> 44:14.986
[ARF ARF]

44:15.053 --> 44:17.655
HA HA HA!

44:22.093 --> 44:23.661
[ARF ARF]

44:27.866 --> 44:29.234
[GROWLING]

44:29.300 --> 44:30.769
WHAT'S HE MAD ABOUT?

44:30.836 --> 44:33.471
HE DON'T LIKE
WHITE FOLKS MUCH.

44:33.538 --> 44:35.573
COME ON, BOY.

44:35.640 --> 44:37.776
COME ON. COME ON.

44:37.843 --> 44:39.978
HERE. FEED HIM THIS.

44:42.347 --> 44:44.783
BOY, YOU ACT LIKE YOU'RE
FEEDING AN ALLIGATOR.

44:44.850 --> 44:46.985
HA HA HA!

44:49.855 --> 44:51.222
HE LOOKS KIND OF MEAN.

44:51.289 --> 44:52.991
WHAT YOU TALKING
ABOUT, MEAN?

44:53.058 --> 44:56.494
HE... HE... HE
JUST PREJUDICED.

44:56.561 --> 44:58.496
HA HA HA!

44:58.563 --> 44:59.998
GOOD BOY.

45:08.539 --> 45:10.008
[BIRD CALLING]

45:55.720 --> 45:57.856
YOU KNOW WHAT,
TOOMER?

45:57.923 --> 46:00.058
THIS IS TERRIFIC.

46:05.430 --> 46:08.133
THERE'S A SHOOTING STAR.

46:10.836 --> 46:12.838
THAT AIN'T
NO STAR, BOY.

46:14.239 --> 46:17.208
THAT'S THE TEAR OF
INFANT JESUS FALLING,

46:17.275 --> 46:23.214
ON ACCOUNT OF IT'S SUCH A
SINFUL AND HATEFUL WORLD.

46:28.686 --> 46:31.556
THIS SURE IS
ONE FINE NIGHT,

46:31.622 --> 46:33.224
AIN'T IT, WHITE BOY?

46:33.291 --> 46:34.893
YEAH.

46:34.960 --> 46:37.795
THIS IS ONE FINE NIGHT.

46:48.073 --> 46:49.774
GOD, THEY'RE ALL
STARING AT US

46:49.841 --> 46:51.142
LIKE WE'RE FREAKS
OR SOMETHING.

46:51.209 --> 46:53.211
NO, THEY'RE NOT.
LOOK.

46:53.278 --> 46:55.746
JUST PICK SOMEONE OUT,
GO ON UP TO THEM AND SAY,

46:55.813 --> 46:58.783
"HI. MY NAME'S
MARY ANNE MEECHUM.

46:58.850 --> 47:02.420
I'M NEW IN TOWN.
I'D LIKE YOU FOR A FRIEND."

47:02.487 --> 47:04.655
WHY DON'T YOU?

47:04.722 --> 47:07.825
LOOK AT THIS.
LOOK AT THIS.

47:09.394 --> 47:12.830
MY, MY, MY,
MY, MY, MY.

47:14.699 --> 47:16.001
IT'S ANSLEY MATTHEWS

47:16.067 --> 47:18.203
AND JIM DON COOPER,
THE VARSITY FULLBACK.

47:18.269 --> 47:19.704
SO WHAT?

47:19.770 --> 47:21.106
JESUS, I'M IN LOVE.

47:21.172 --> 47:22.373
HAVE YOU TOLD HIM YET?

47:22.440 --> 47:24.642
THAT'S FUNNY.
VERY FUNNY.

47:24.709 --> 47:28.846
MR. AND MRS.
NEANDERTHAL. CUTE.

47:35.453 --> 47:37.255
HEY, SHAKE IT OUT, HOG.

47:37.322 --> 47:38.023
LET'S GO.

47:38.089 --> 47:40.658
WHAT'S THE MATTER?

47:40.725 --> 47:43.962
GOD, DAD, IT'S 4:00.

47:44.029 --> 47:46.864
HAPPY BIRTHDAY, BOY.

47:50.035 --> 47:51.436
YOU WOKE ME UP
AT 4 A.M.

47:51.502 --> 47:53.404
TO GIVE ME
MY BIRTHDAY PRESENT.

47:53.471 --> 47:55.340
MM-HMM.

47:57.375 --> 47:59.177
THAT'S GREAT.

48:00.745 --> 48:02.380
WHAT IS IT?

48:03.881 --> 48:06.184
IT'S A TRAINING BRA.
OPEN IT.

48:06.251 --> 48:09.887
I'VE BEEN SAVING IT
FOR YOU FOR 18 YEARS.

48:22.467 --> 48:24.102
LOOKS GOOD.

48:24.169 --> 48:25.403
THAT WAS MY FIRST.

48:25.470 --> 48:29.174
I WORE IT IN WWII WHEN
I FLEW WITH THE COBRAS.

48:29.240 --> 48:31.776
IT'S GREAT, DAD.
THANKS.

48:31.842 --> 48:34.512
THEY DON'T MAKE THEM
LIKE THAT ANYMORE.

48:34.579 --> 48:37.215
IT'S PART OF THE OLD CORPS.

48:42.087 --> 48:45.223
CHRIST, YOU'RE 18, BEN.

48:48.193 --> 48:51.029
I WOKE UP THINKING ABOUT
THE DAY YOU WERE BORN.

48:51.096 --> 48:54.532
I WAS ON A HOP, AND ALL
I HEARD WHEN I LANDED

48:54.599 --> 48:57.035
WAS THAT YOUR MOTHER
WAS IN A HOSPITAL.

48:57.102 --> 48:58.536
SO I WENT CRAZY.

48:58.603 --> 49:01.872
I HIT 100 MILES AN HOUR
GETTING THERE,

49:01.939 --> 49:04.942
KNOCKING NURSES
OUT OF THE WAY,

49:05.010 --> 49:05.810
RUNNING OVER
THE SMALL CHILDREN,

49:05.876 --> 49:06.978
CRASHING INTO PATIENTS

49:07.045 --> 49:12.217
ON THE WAY
TO THE OPERATING ROOM.

49:12.283 --> 49:15.853
AND YOU'RE SCREAMING
YOUR HEAD OFF.

49:15.920 --> 49:19.324
I'M BANGING ON THE WINDOW
TRYING TO GET YOUR ATTENTION,

49:19.390 --> 49:21.726
BRAGGING TO EVERYBODY
WHO'D LISTEN

49:21.792 --> 49:24.395
THAT THE TOUGHEST LITTLE
FIGHTER PILOT IN THE WORLD

49:24.462 --> 49:26.564
HAD BEEN BORN.

49:27.999 --> 49:29.867
THEN I RAN DOWN TO SEE
HOW YOUR MOTHER WAS,

49:29.934 --> 49:31.869
EXPECTING HER
TO LOOK LIKE, UH...

49:31.936 --> 49:35.973
HORSESHIT FROM HELL AFTER
PUNCHING YOU OUT OF HER SYSTEM.

49:36.774 --> 49:39.077
HELL, SHE WAS SITTING UP,

49:39.144 --> 49:41.979
LOOKING PRETTIER
THAN I'D EVER SEEN HER.

49:44.115 --> 49:46.284
HA HA!

49:47.252 --> 49:49.454
THAT WAS 18 YEARS AGO.

49:49.520 --> 49:52.090
18 YEARS AGO TODAY.

49:52.157 --> 49:54.992
I WAS 23.

49:59.264 --> 50:01.999
THAT WAS SOME DAY.

50:11.709 --> 50:15.780
I GOT TO REGISTER FOR THE
DRAFT WITHIN 10 DAYS.

50:15.846 --> 50:18.183
I'LL TAKE YOU DOWN.

50:22.120 --> 50:23.788
I WANT YOU TO MEET ME
AT THE CLUB AT 1700

50:23.854 --> 50:25.490
FOR A LITTLE
CELEBRATION, O.K.?

50:25.556 --> 50:26.291
O.K.

50:26.357 --> 50:27.492
TELL MAMMA
WE'LL BE HOME

50:27.558 --> 50:30.628
FOR SUPPER AND
THE CAKE CUTTING AT 1830.

50:30.695 --> 50:32.430
WEAR A COAT AND TIE.

50:32.497 --> 50:34.699
YES, SIR.

50:34.765 --> 50:36.134
GO BACK TO SLEEP.

50:36.201 --> 50:38.035
[CLOSES DOOR]

50:47.778 --> 50:49.347
[SPEAKING FRENCH]

50:55.320 --> 50:58.656
[LILLIAN]
MY DEAR SON, MY DEAR BEN,

50:58.723 --> 51:02.960
MY DEAR FRIEND
WHO BECOMES A MAN TODAY.

51:03.027 --> 51:06.664
I WANTED TO WRITE YOU
A LETTER ABOUT BEING A MAN

51:06.731 --> 51:10.067
AND WHAT THAT MEANS
IN A FULLER SENSE.

51:10.135 --> 51:11.736
I WANTED TO TELL YOU

51:11.802 --> 51:15.740
THAT GENTLENESS IS THE QUALITY
I MOST ADMIRED IN MEN,

51:15.806 --> 51:18.843
AND THEN I REMEMBERED
HOW GENTLE YOU WERE,

51:18.909 --> 51:22.046
SO I DECIDED TO WRITE
SOMETHING ELSE.

51:22.113 --> 51:24.615
IT'S JUST THIS...

51:24.682 --> 51:27.452
I WANT YOU TO KNOW
THAT WHATEVER YOU DO

51:27.518 --> 51:29.754
OR WHEREVER YOU GO,

51:29.820 --> 51:33.924
YOU WALK WITH
MY BLESSING AND LOVE.

51:33.991 --> 51:39.130
I'VE HAD MY REGRETS
AND MANY SADNESSES,

51:39.197 --> 51:43.033
BUT I WILL NEVER REGRET
THE NIGHT YOU WERE BORN.

51:43.100 --> 51:47.438
I THOUGHT I KNEW ABOUT LOVE
AND THE BOUNDARIES OF LOVE

51:47.505 --> 51:51.476
UNTIL I RAISED YOU
FOR THESE PAST 18 YEARS.

51:51.542 --> 51:54.945
I KNEW NOTHING ABOUT LOVE.

51:55.012 --> 51:58.015
THIS HAS BEEN YOUR GIFT TO ME.

51:58.082 --> 52:02.119
HAPPY BIRTHDAY. MAMMA.

52:19.170 --> 52:22.139
HEY, SPORTS FAN,
OVER HERE.

52:33.218 --> 52:36.120
WHAT THE HELL
YOU GRINNING ABOUT?

52:36.187 --> 52:37.755
THIS IS REALLY MY DAY.

52:37.822 --> 52:39.123
I MADE THE VARSITY TEAM.

52:39.190 --> 52:40.458
OF COURSE YOU DID.

52:40.525 --> 52:43.027
YOU ONLY HAD THE GREATEST
COACH IN THE WORLD.

52:43.093 --> 52:45.696
CONGRATULATIONS ON YOUR 18th.

52:45.763 --> 52:47.064
THANKS, COLONEL.

52:47.131 --> 52:48.333
WHAT WILL YOU HAVE?

52:48.399 --> 52:50.835
DR. PEPPER.

52:50.901 --> 52:53.904
I DIDN'T BRING YOU
DOWN HERE TO DRINK SODA POP.

52:53.971 --> 52:55.840
YOU'RE OLD ENOUGH
TO DRINK NOW.

52:55.906 --> 52:57.408
MOM WILL GET MAD, DAD.

52:57.475 --> 52:59.310
BESIDES, I'M
IN TRAINING NOW.

52:59.377 --> 53:00.878
IF HE DOESN'T
WANT TO DRINK...

53:00.945 --> 53:04.014
THERE'S THOSE THAT GOT THEM,
AND THOSE THAT DON'T.

53:04.081 --> 53:05.483
WHAT?

53:05.550 --> 53:08.419
GONADS, SON.
BIG BRASS ONES.

53:09.854 --> 53:16.327
BARTENDER, I'LL HAVE A DOUBLE
MARTINI UP WITH A TWIST.

53:17.328 --> 53:19.630
DO YOU KNOW WHAT
A DOUBLE MARTINI IS?

53:19.697 --> 53:20.998
SURE.

53:21.065 --> 53:23.100
WILL YOU LEAVE
HIM ALONE?

53:23.167 --> 53:25.603
IT'S MADE OUT OF LIQUOR.

53:25.670 --> 53:26.937
YOU BET.

53:27.004 --> 53:29.440
YOU GOT
AN I.D., SON?

53:29.507 --> 53:32.510
SURE, I GOT AN I.D.

53:41.319 --> 53:43.521
HAPPY BIRTHDAY, KID.

53:51.462 --> 53:54.031
JUST A MINUTE, BEN.

53:54.098 --> 53:55.266
GENTLEMEN!

53:55.333 --> 53:57.001
GENTLEMEN...

53:57.067 --> 53:58.202
I WOULD LIKE YOU

53:58.269 --> 54:01.038
TO JOIN ME IN A TOAST
TO MY OLDEST SON,

54:01.105 --> 54:03.107
WHO'S 18 TODAY.

54:03.173 --> 54:05.009
HE JUST ORDERED
HIS FIRST DRINK.

54:05.075 --> 54:07.144
BEFORE HE BEGINS
DRINKING IT,

54:07.211 --> 54:09.980
I WOULD LIKE TO
WISH HIM A LONG LIFE,

54:10.047 --> 54:12.983
A WIFE AS FINE
AS HIS MOTHER,

54:13.050 --> 54:17.087
AND A SON AS FINE
AS HE'S BEEN.

54:17.154 --> 54:18.656
TO MY SON.

54:18.723 --> 54:21.058
[CROWD]
HAPPY BIRTHDAY!

54:21.125 --> 54:22.360
HEAR! HEAR!

54:22.427 --> 54:24.161
CONGRATULATIONS.

54:24.228 --> 54:26.564
CONGRATULATIONS,
KID.

54:32.136 --> 54:33.571
[BULL LAUGHING]

54:36.407 --> 54:41.011
HOW IS IT, BIG MAN?

54:41.078 --> 54:44.014
IT'S FIT TO DRINK,
BUT I'VE TASTED BETTER.

54:46.684 --> 54:51.288
BARTENDER,
LET'S HAVE ANOTHER HERE.

54:53.458 --> 54:55.292
[LAUGHTER]

55:12.677 --> 55:15.813
SLOW DOWN, BEN.
THAT'S AN ALLIGATOR OF A DRINK.

55:15.880 --> 55:17.882
THAT'S WHY
I ORDERED IT, VIRGIL.

55:17.948 --> 55:20.250
IT'S COLONEL HEDGEPATH
TO YOU, MISTER.

55:20.317 --> 55:23.253
SIR. SIR, MY APOLOGIES.

55:23.320 --> 55:24.589
HEY.

55:24.655 --> 55:29.627
THIS IS GREAT,
REALLY GREAT.

55:32.497 --> 55:34.565
HEY, WAITER,
ANOTHER DRINK FOR MY SON.

55:34.632 --> 55:36.601
LILLIAN'S GOING
TO SCALP YOU, BULL.

55:36.667 --> 55:38.736
HECK, VIRG, COME ON.

55:38.803 --> 55:42.640
I DON'T EVEN HAVE
A BUZZ ON YET.

55:42.707 --> 55:43.908
GOD.

55:43.974 --> 55:45.443
HEY! HEY!

55:45.510 --> 55:46.511
THIS IS REALLY GREAT, DAD.

55:46.577 --> 55:47.645
YOU LIKE IT, HUH?

55:47.712 --> 55:51.348
REALLY GREAT,
REALLY GREAT.

55:52.182 --> 55:54.885
SOBER UP, DAD.

55:54.952 --> 55:55.853
DRINK UP, SON.

55:55.920 --> 55:57.688
DRINK UP, HUH?

55:57.755 --> 55:59.023
YOU KNOW WHAT
I WAS THINKING?

55:59.089 --> 56:01.358
WHAT?

56:01.426 --> 56:03.561
I THINK
IT'S REALLY GREAT.

56:03.628 --> 56:04.862
I THINK IT'S GREAT.

56:04.929 --> 56:08.666
VIRG, VIRG,
I THINK THIS IS GREAT.

56:08.733 --> 56:10.100
DAD?

56:10.167 --> 56:11.902
GREAT! GOD!

56:11.969 --> 56:13.404
WHAT ABOUT IT? HUH?

56:13.471 --> 56:16.941
DAD. HEY, DAD.

56:17.007 --> 56:18.443
O.K. ALMOST.

56:18.509 --> 56:19.644
HERE THEY COME!

56:19.710 --> 56:21.879
OH, MY GOSH.
TURN OUT THE LIGHT, QUICK!

56:21.946 --> 56:23.714
WHEN I SAY "NOW,"

56:23.781 --> 56:26.851
TURN ON THE LIGHTS,
AND THEN WE START SINGING.

56:26.917 --> 56:28.352
COME ON, NOW.

56:28.419 --> 56:30.688
OH, FOR HEAVEN'S...
I BLEW ONE OUT.

56:30.755 --> 56:32.757
LOOK AT THAT.
ISN'T THAT SILLY?

56:32.823 --> 56:34.158
THEY WON'T
GO FAST ENOUGH

56:34.224 --> 56:35.560
WHEN YOU NEED THEM TO,
DO THEY?

56:35.626 --> 56:38.128
GET DOWN QUICKLY.

56:38.195 --> 56:39.329
NOW.

56:39.396 --> 56:43.167
♪ HAPPY BIRTHDAY TO YOU ♪

56:43.233 --> 56:45.002
♪ HAPPY... ♪

56:46.437 --> 56:50.675
ON BEHALF OF MY ILLUSTRIOUS,
THOUGH SOMEWHAT INEBRIATED SON,

56:50.741 --> 56:52.877
I THANK YOU
FOR THIS JOYOUS DISPLAY.

56:52.943 --> 56:56.280
HOWEVER,
AS THE HOUR IS LATE

56:56.346 --> 56:57.515
AND SEEING AS HOW BEN

56:57.582 --> 57:01.686
MADE THE VARSITY
BASKETBALL TEAM TODAY,

57:01.752 --> 57:05.222
HE IS IN TRAINING,
BADLY IN NEED OF REST.

57:05.289 --> 57:07.157
THEREFORE,

57:07.224 --> 57:08.593
I WILL TAKE HIM TO BED

57:08.659 --> 57:12.029
WHERE HE CAN PARTAKE
OF SAME STRAIGHTAWAY.

57:12.096 --> 57:16.734
THANK YOU ALL...
AND WE LOVE YOU.

57:18.235 --> 57:22.573
♪ HAPPY BIRTHDAY,
SON OF SANTINI ♪

57:22.640 --> 57:26.644
♪ HAPPY BIRTHDAY TO YOU ♪

57:33.350 --> 57:34.719
YOU KNOW, LIL,
HE'S GOT IT ALL.

57:34.785 --> 57:36.220
HE'S FAST.
HE'S GOT BALANCE.

57:36.286 --> 57:38.523
HE'S GOT SMARTS.

57:38.589 --> 57:41.358
I THINK YOU GENTLE HIM TOO MUCH.

57:41.425 --> 57:44.461
IT SCREWS UP HIS INSTINCTS
AND HIS TIMING.

57:44.529 --> 57:45.796
IF THERE'S
ONE THING

57:45.863 --> 57:46.897
I WANT TO
GIVE MY SONS,

57:46.964 --> 57:48.132
IT'S THE GIFT
OF FURY.

57:48.198 --> 57:49.600
I WANT THEM TO
GOBBLE UP THE WORLD,

57:49.667 --> 57:54.939
EAT LIFE,
OR IT WILL EAT THEM.

57:55.005 --> 57:57.675
LIL?

57:59.343 --> 58:00.678
LILLIAN?

58:08.385 --> 58:09.654
[TOOMER]
SO THIS FELLA SAYS,

58:09.720 --> 58:12.757
"WHO WAS THAT WOMAN
I SEEN YOU WITH LAST NIGHT?"

58:12.823 --> 58:15.760
HE SAY, "SHE ONE
OF THE LEE SISTERS."

58:15.826 --> 58:18.763
"YEAH? THEN HER FIRST NAME
MUST BE UG."

58:18.829 --> 58:20.965
[BEN]
UG. I GET IT.

58:21.031 --> 58:22.266
[LAUGHING]

58:36.146 --> 58:39.283
WHAT YOU DANCING AROUND
LIKE THAT FOR?

58:40.851 --> 58:43.554
A BEE AIN'T GONNA
MESS WITH YOU.

58:43.621 --> 58:45.790
HE DOING HIS JOB.

58:45.856 --> 58:49.093
SEE, THE BEE'S
LIKE THE PREACHER MAN.

58:49.159 --> 58:54.799
HE GO FROM THE GIRL FLOWER
TO THE BOY FLOWER,

58:54.865 --> 58:57.802
AND EVERYWHERE HE TOUCH,
THEY BE MARRIED,

58:57.868 --> 59:03.407
AND THEY SAY,
"THANK YOU, PREACHER BEE.

59:03.473 --> 59:05.943
"HERE, WHY DON'T YOU
HAVE SOME HONEY

59:06.010 --> 59:07.444
FOR YOUR PAY?"

59:07.511 --> 59:11.448
AND THAT'S
THE PERFECT WAY OF IT.

59:11.515 --> 59:16.453
TOOMER, YOU ARE A
POET, YOU KNOW THAT?

59:16.520 --> 59:20.457
WELL, AIN'T EVERY
NATURAL BORN LIAR?

59:20.524 --> 59:21.959
[LAUGHING]

59:35.973 --> 59:38.508
WELL, I'LL SEE YOU FOLKS
WITH THE SUN.

59:38.575 --> 59:39.509
GOOD LUCK, BEN.

59:39.576 --> 59:40.645
THANK YOU,
ARRABELLE.

59:40.711 --> 59:41.679
GOOD NIGHT,
MISS MEECHUM.

59:41.746 --> 59:42.980
GOOD NIGHT.

59:43.047 --> 59:46.516
BETTER CHECK HER PURSE
FOR THE SILVER.

59:46.583 --> 59:47.918
GOOD NIGHT, CAPTAIN.

59:47.985 --> 59:49.754
GOOD NIGHT,
ARRABELLE.

59:49.820 --> 59:52.957
MEECHUM SEES HIS MOTHER
MAKING AN APPLE PIE,

59:53.023 --> 59:54.391
DRIBBLES LEFT.

59:54.458 --> 59:56.794
THERE'S DAD,
READING THE NEWSPAPER.

59:56.861 --> 59:59.296
GET OFF YOUR FEET.
GO TAKE A NAP.

59:59.363 --> 01:00:00.497
THIS HELPS ME RELAX.

01:00:00.564 --> 01:00:02.867
IT DOESN'T HELP ME RELAX!
SCRAM!

01:00:02.933 --> 01:00:04.534
I COULDN'T SLEEP
LAST NIGHT.

01:00:04.601 --> 01:00:06.671
I WAS SO WORRIED
ABOUT THE BIG GAME.

01:00:06.737 --> 01:00:08.773
I WOKE UP
IN A COLD SWEAT

01:00:08.839 --> 01:00:12.710
WITH A FEVER AND THREE
TYPES OF CANCER

01:00:12.777 --> 01:00:14.779
AND A TOUCH
OF RABIES!

01:00:14.845 --> 01:00:16.747
DAD, I GOT AN "A"
ON MY ENGLISH THEME.

01:00:16.814 --> 01:00:17.882
WOULD YOU READ IT?

01:00:17.948 --> 01:00:19.183
I'M READING
MY PAPER.

01:00:19.249 --> 01:00:20.785
DAD, I CAN EAT
A WHOLE CAN OF PEACHES

01:00:20.851 --> 01:00:22.519
IN LESS
THAN 60 SECONDS.

01:00:22.586 --> 01:00:24.855
WANT TO BET ME?

01:00:24.922 --> 01:00:26.323
WOULD YOU TWO
PLEASE GO UPSTAIRS

01:00:26.390 --> 01:00:27.725
AND DO YOUR HOMEWORK

01:00:27.792 --> 01:00:30.560
SO YOU'LL HAVE IT DONE
BEFORE THE GAME?

01:00:30.627 --> 01:00:34.031
GO ON NOW.

01:00:36.133 --> 01:00:40.037
YOUR FATHER IS VERY
NERVOUS ABOUT THIS GAME.

01:00:40.905 --> 01:00:43.640
LOOK AT ME,
YOUNG LADY.

01:00:43.708 --> 01:00:46.643
YOU'VE GOT TO
LEARN TO INTERPRET

01:00:46.711 --> 01:00:48.979
THE SIGNALS
HE GIVES OFF.

01:00:49.046 --> 01:00:49.914
HE ALWAYS GIVES OFF
THE SIGNALS

01:00:49.980 --> 01:00:51.248
OF A PSYCHOPATHIC KILLER,

01:00:51.315 --> 01:00:54.985
SO IT DOESN'T MATTER
HOW YOU INTERPRET THEM.

01:00:55.619 --> 01:00:58.055
SHAME ON YOU!

01:01:08.098 --> 01:01:10.134
HEY, DAD,
WHY DO YOU LOVE ME

01:01:10.200 --> 01:01:12.236
MORE THAN
YOUR OTHER CHILDREN?

01:01:12.302 --> 01:01:15.672
BEAT IT. I'M READING
THE SPORTS PAGE.

01:01:15.740 --> 01:01:18.075
LET'S HAVE
A CONVERSATION, DAD.

01:01:18.142 --> 01:01:20.811
LET'S BARE OUR SOULS
AND KNOW ONE ANOTHER.

01:01:20.878 --> 01:01:22.412
I DON'T WANT YOU
TO GET TO KNOW ME.

01:01:22.479 --> 01:01:23.748
I LIKE
BEING AN ENIGMA,

01:01:23.814 --> 01:01:26.183
LIKE A CHINK.

01:01:26.250 --> 01:01:31.021
AM I A MEECHUM, DAD?
CAN GIRLS BE REAL MEECHUMS?

01:01:31.088 --> 01:01:33.958
GIRLS WITHOUT JUMP SHOTS?

01:01:34.024 --> 01:01:36.326
OR AM I A SIMPLE FORM
OF MEECHUM

01:01:36.393 --> 01:01:37.728
LIKE IN BIOLOGY?

01:01:37.795 --> 01:01:40.664
MARY ANNE,
THE ONE-CELLED MEECHUM.

01:01:40.731 --> 01:01:41.899
MARY ANNE, SCRAM.

01:01:41.966 --> 01:01:43.600
I'M STARTING
TO LOSE MY TEMPER!

01:01:43.667 --> 01:01:46.804
LILLIAN!

01:01:46.871 --> 01:01:50.040
DAD, I'M PREGNANT.

01:01:50.107 --> 01:01:53.210
I'M PREGNANT
BY A NEGRO, DADDY.

01:01:53.277 --> 01:01:54.644
HIS NAME IS RUFUS.

01:01:54.711 --> 01:01:56.080
I DIDN'T WANT TO TELL YOU,

01:01:56.146 --> 01:02:00.250
BUT SINCE WE'RE BARING
OUR SOULS TO EACH OTHER,

01:02:00.317 --> 01:02:03.087
RUFUS IS A PACIFIST...

01:02:03.788 --> 01:02:06.190
A PACIFIST HOMOSEXUAL.

01:02:06.256 --> 01:02:07.657
JESUS H. CHRIST!

01:02:07.724 --> 01:02:10.527
LILLIAN,
I'M GOING TO THE CLUB.

01:02:10.594 --> 01:02:11.929
I'LL SEE YOU ALL
AT THE GAME.

01:02:11.996 --> 01:02:13.931
CAN'T STAND IT
AROUND HERE!

01:02:13.998 --> 01:02:16.100
YOU'LL GET TO LIKE HIM
AFTER A WHILE, DAD.

01:02:16.166 --> 01:02:17.734
DWARVES
ARE EASY TO LIKE,

01:02:17.802 --> 01:02:19.136
ESPECIALLY
WHEN THEY'RE BALD

01:02:19.203 --> 01:02:20.370
AND CROSS-EYED.

01:02:20.437 --> 01:02:23.140
DAD. DAD.

01:02:23.207 --> 01:02:24.074
DAD!

01:02:24.141 --> 01:02:29.646
JIM DON, I HEAR
LOU ELLEN ALSTON

01:02:29.713 --> 01:02:32.749
HAS GOT THE HOT
UTERUS FOR YOU.

01:02:32.817 --> 01:02:34.318
BEN!

01:02:35.319 --> 01:02:36.620
THERE ARE SCOUTS
OUT THERE

01:02:36.686 --> 01:02:39.056
FROM FOUR
DIFFERENT COLLEGES.

01:02:39.123 --> 01:02:40.624
WE'RE TRYING TO
GET READY, DAD.

01:02:40.690 --> 01:02:42.526
WE WANT
40 BIG ONES.

01:02:42.592 --> 01:02:43.828
WE'LL HELP HIM.

01:02:43.894 --> 01:02:45.429
ATTA-BOY, ART.

01:02:45.495 --> 01:02:46.363
THE BEST
BALLPLAYERS

01:02:46.430 --> 01:02:49.834
HAVE THEIR
GREATEST GAMES

01:02:49.900 --> 01:02:52.736
AGAINST
THE BEST TEAMS.

01:02:52.803 --> 01:02:54.471
THANKS, DAD.

01:02:54.538 --> 01:02:56.874
SEE YOU
OUT THERE.

01:02:58.475 --> 01:03:00.777
OOH-WEE.

01:03:02.546 --> 01:03:04.748
HE GETS EXCITED
AT TIMES LIKE THIS.

01:03:04.815 --> 01:03:06.183
YOU THINK HE'S EXCITED?

01:03:06.250 --> 01:03:09.719
MY DAD HASN'T TAKEN A CRAP
FOR THREE DAYS.

01:03:09.786 --> 01:03:11.889
BOY,
HE'S REALLY TANKED UP.

01:03:11.956 --> 01:03:13.590
NAH,
HE'S JUST EXCITED.

01:03:13.657 --> 01:03:16.126
SHIT. I KNOW A DRUNK
WHEN I SEE ONE.

01:03:16.193 --> 01:03:19.997
O.K. O.K. O.K.
SHUT THAT THING OFF.

01:03:20.064 --> 01:03:22.799
YOU GUYS,
GET YOUR BUNS AROUND HERE.

01:03:22.867 --> 01:03:25.035
ALL RIGHT, COACH.

01:03:29.940 --> 01:03:33.443
I WANT YOU BOYS
TO HIT THAT COURT HUNGRY.

01:03:33.510 --> 01:03:35.079
I WANT YOU STARVING.

01:03:35.145 --> 01:03:38.715
I WANT US TO WIN
AND WIN BIG!

01:03:38.782 --> 01:03:41.718
I WANT TO MAKE
OUR SCHOOL PROUD.

01:03:41.785 --> 01:03:43.854
I WANT TO MAKE
OUR PARENTS PROUD,

01:03:43.921 --> 01:03:45.722
OUR GRANDPARENTS PROUD,

01:03:45.789 --> 01:03:48.025
OUR FIRST AND SECOND COUSINS
PROUD,

01:03:48.092 --> 01:03:51.195
OUR POONTANG PROUD,
AND OURSELVES PROUD!

01:03:51.261 --> 01:03:53.197
YOU HEAR WHAT I'M SAYING?

01:03:53.263 --> 01:03:54.664
YES, SIR!
YES, SIR!

01:03:54.731 --> 01:03:58.002
GET OUT THERE
AND EAT THEM UP!

01:03:58.068 --> 01:04:00.637
GO! GO! GO! GO!

01:04:00.704 --> 01:04:04.108
[PLAYING MARINE'S HYMN]

01:04:30.334 --> 01:04:32.269
[BUZZER]

01:04:45.815 --> 01:04:47.384
EAGLES! EAGLES!

01:04:47.451 --> 01:04:50.120
YOU AIN'T GOING TO
SCORE, MEECHUM.

01:04:50.187 --> 01:04:52.056
I'LL BE ON YOU
LIKE STINK ON SHIT.

01:04:52.122 --> 01:04:54.291
STINK IS THE WORD.

01:05:00.897 --> 01:05:03.033
BEAUTIFUL.

01:05:11.875 --> 01:05:13.477
HEY, THAT'S A FOUL!

01:05:13.543 --> 01:05:16.013
FOUL!

01:05:23.887 --> 01:05:26.156
PLAY SOME DEFENSE!

01:05:50.981 --> 01:05:53.550
THAT'S A FOUL.

01:05:53.617 --> 01:05:56.253
FOUL!

01:05:56.320 --> 01:06:00.457
WE'LL TAKE THREE
ON THAT ONE, REF.

01:06:00.524 --> 01:06:02.626
OH, OH, OH!

01:06:13.770 --> 01:06:15.405
[BUZZER]

01:06:17.407 --> 01:06:19.476
THAT'S O.K.
WE'LL GET THE SECOND HALF.

01:06:19.543 --> 01:06:21.978
HANGING IN THERE.
I'M PROUD OF YOU.

01:06:22.046 --> 01:06:26.350
YOU'RE DOING A GOOD JOB.

01:06:28.752 --> 01:06:29.619
T...

01:06:29.686 --> 01:06:30.654
E...

01:06:30.720 --> 01:06:31.388
A...

01:06:31.455 --> 01:06:32.456
M.

01:06:32.522 --> 01:06:35.259
[CHEERING]

01:07:06.323 --> 01:07:09.993
LOOK AT THAT
SON OF A BITCH!

01:07:10.060 --> 01:07:11.461
[BOOING]

01:07:17.667 --> 01:07:21.938
THAT'S A FOUL!
LET'S GET WITH IT, REF!

01:07:22.005 --> 01:07:24.241
LET'S GET WITH IT!
FOUL!

01:07:24.741 --> 01:07:27.444
BOO!

01:07:40.657 --> 01:07:43.026
[PLAYS CALL TO ARMS]

01:07:43.093 --> 01:07:44.027
CHARGE!

01:07:44.094 --> 01:07:45.028
♪ ♪

01:07:45.095 --> 01:07:46.496
CHARGE!

01:07:46.563 --> 01:07:47.597
♪ ♪

01:07:47.664 --> 01:07:49.199
CHARGE!

01:07:56.640 --> 01:07:59.643
[WHISTLE BLOWS]

01:07:59.709 --> 01:08:00.444
FOUL. ONE SHOT.

01:08:00.510 --> 01:08:02.979
LET'S GO.

01:08:03.046 --> 01:08:04.148
MEECHUM, I'M TAKING
YOU OUT OF THIS GAME

01:08:04.214 --> 01:08:06.583
BULLDOZER STYLE.

01:08:06.650 --> 01:08:08.084
IT'S A SHAME
THE REST OF YOU

01:08:08.152 --> 01:08:15.192
DON'T WORK AS GOOD
AS YOUR MOUTH.

01:08:19.196 --> 01:08:22.631
THAT'S A FOUL!
THAT'S A FOUL!

01:08:26.236 --> 01:08:28.104
[BOOING]

01:08:31.541 --> 01:08:33.877
THEY DID IT
ON PURPOSE.

01:08:33.943 --> 01:08:35.279
YOU O.K., MEECHUM?

01:08:35.345 --> 01:08:36.078
SURE,
I'M FINE.

01:08:36.145 --> 01:08:38.182
GIVE HIM SOME AIR.

01:08:38.247 --> 01:08:40.450
GET THAT PUNK.
PUT HIM ON THE DECK.

01:08:40.517 --> 01:08:42.319
YOU GET HIM,
OR I'LL GET YOU.

01:08:42.386 --> 01:08:48.591
GET HIM,
OR YOU DON'T COME HOME.

01:09:23.091 --> 01:09:25.194
GET HIM!
PUT HIM ON THE DECK!

01:09:25.261 --> 01:09:27.897
NUMBER 25!

01:09:27.964 --> 01:09:30.300
NUMBER 25, YOU GOT TO
PUT HIM ON THE FLOOR,

01:09:30.367 --> 01:09:32.402
OR DON'T COME HOME
TONIGHT!

01:09:32.469 --> 01:09:35.104
YOU HEAR ME?
PUT HIM DOWN, BENNY!

01:09:35.171 --> 01:09:41.377
PUT HIM DOWN!

01:10:17.146 --> 01:10:21.318
ABBOTT'S GOT A BROKEN
ARM, PISS ANT.

01:10:21.385 --> 01:10:22.218
THEY'RE
OUT THERE

01:10:22.286 --> 01:10:26.122
BEATING
OUR TAILS OFF.

01:10:26.189 --> 01:10:28.792
I'M SORRY.

01:10:28.858 --> 01:10:31.395
GOD. I'M SORRY.

01:10:31.461 --> 01:10:34.598
YOU MESSED UP BAD,
BOY.

01:10:34.664 --> 01:10:38.735
I KNOW.

01:10:38.802 --> 01:10:40.837
THIS TEAM
HAD A CHANCE TONIGHT

01:10:40.904 --> 01:10:45.609
AGAINST A SCHOOL THAT'S BEEN
CRAPPIN' ON US FOR 10 YEARS.

01:10:45.675 --> 01:10:47.076
THEN ALONG COMES
THIS IDIOT

01:10:47.143 --> 01:10:47.944
WHO HASN'T
GOT THE GUTS

01:10:48.011 --> 01:10:48.978
TO TELL HIS FATHER

01:10:49.045 --> 01:10:50.146
TO TAKE
A FLYING JUMP

01:10:50.213 --> 01:10:52.349
WHEN THAT FATHER'S
WRONG.

01:10:52.416 --> 01:10:54.984
WHAT DO YOU THINK
I OUGHT TO DO?

01:10:55.051 --> 01:10:56.085
KILL ME.

01:10:56.152 --> 01:10:57.220
DO YOU
THINK IT'S FAIR

01:10:57.287 --> 01:11:00.156
IF I DUMP YOU
FROM THE TEAM?

01:11:00.223 --> 01:11:01.725
YES, SIR.

01:11:01.791 --> 01:11:04.494
WELL, I DON'T!

01:11:06.195 --> 01:11:11.635
I DON'T THINK IT'S A FAIR
EXCHANGE FOR A BROKEN ARM.

01:11:11.701 --> 01:11:16.840
BUT WE'RE JUST GOING
TO LEAVE IT LIKE THAT.

01:11:31.788 --> 01:11:34.724
[SINGING]

01:11:36.460 --> 01:11:37.661
HI, TOOMER.

01:11:37.727 --> 01:11:40.096
HEY.

01:11:40.163 --> 01:11:43.266
HEY, TOOMER.
HOW YOU DOING?

01:11:43.333 --> 01:11:46.035
GOOD MORNING,
TOOMER.

01:11:46.102 --> 01:11:48.071
I NEED TWO...

01:11:48.805 --> 01:11:49.339
P-P-P-PAILS.

01:11:49.406 --> 01:11:51.975
RIGHT THERE.

01:11:52.041 --> 01:11:54.511
I BRUNG FOUR JARS
OF HONEY.

01:11:54.578 --> 01:11:56.480
PUT THEM
ON THE BENCH.

01:11:56.546 --> 01:11:59.616
I NEVER HEARD
OF A P-P-P-PAIL BEFORE.

01:11:59.683 --> 01:12:02.686
WHAT'S THAT, TOOMER?
SOME KIND OF NEW WORD?

01:12:02.752 --> 01:12:03.887
I HEAR YOUR FRIEND
MEECHUM

01:12:03.953 --> 01:12:09.325
GOT KICKED OFF
THE TEAM FOR GOOD.

01:12:09.393 --> 01:12:10.527
YOU TWO HAVE BEEN
TIGHT AS TICKS.

01:12:10.594 --> 01:12:14.398
I FIGURED
IT MUST BE LOVE.

01:12:15.298 --> 01:12:16.700
HERE.
LET ME HELP YOU.

01:12:16.766 --> 01:12:20.336
I DON'T NEED
NO HELP FROM YOU.

01:12:20.404 --> 01:12:24.007
Y-Y-Y-YOU DON'T?

01:12:25.375 --> 01:12:30.447
ALL RIGHT, THEN.
I WON'T HELP YOU.

01:12:43.493 --> 01:12:47.964
THERE'S TWO MORE JARS.
HERE'S THE DIFFERENCE.

01:12:48.031 --> 01:12:49.466
[GLASS BREAKING]

01:12:51.568 --> 01:12:56.072
LET IT GO, TOOMER.
IT JUST AIN'T WORTH IT.

01:13:05.815 --> 01:13:09.419
DAMN, THAT'S CLUMSY
OF ME, TOOMER.

01:13:10.620 --> 01:13:12.589
I WAS JUST TRYING TO
BE A GOOD NEIGHBOR.

01:13:12.656 --> 01:13:18.795
Y-Y-YOU AIN'T M-M-MAD
AT ME, ARE YOU?

01:13:24.634 --> 01:13:26.402
YOU MOVE, RED,

01:13:26.470 --> 01:13:29.439
AND I'LL TELL MAN O' WAR
TO GO,

01:13:29.506 --> 01:13:32.275
AND SHE'LL TAKE
YOUR HEAD WITH HER.

01:13:32.341 --> 01:13:33.443
HEY, NIGGER!

01:13:33.510 --> 01:13:37.614
DON'T TOUCH HIM!
HE'LL DO IT!

01:13:38.615 --> 01:13:42.519
LET HIM GO, TOOMER.
JUST DO IT, SON.

01:13:42.586 --> 01:13:45.188
NONE OF THESE BOYS
ARE GOING TO HURT YOU.

01:13:45.254 --> 01:13:47.891
GO ON.

01:13:55.465 --> 01:13:57.601
I'LL GET YOU,
YOU GIMP NIGGER!

01:13:57.667 --> 01:14:00.470
I'LL GET YOU FOR THAT!
I'LL GET YOU, YOU HEAR?

01:14:00.537 --> 01:14:01.605
YOU HEAR ME?

01:14:01.671 --> 01:14:05.575
YOU MAKE ME SICK,
PETTUS.

01:14:05.642 --> 01:14:08.344
I'LL GET YOU, TOOMER!
YOU HEAR ME TALKING TO YOU?

01:14:08.411 --> 01:14:09.078
TOOMER!

01:14:09.145 --> 01:14:10.346
GET UP.

01:14:10.413 --> 01:14:11.948
TOOMER!

01:14:12.015 --> 01:14:15.485
LOOK AT ME!

01:14:16.720 --> 01:14:20.624
THANKS A LOT, PINKIE.
GUYS. SEE YOU.

01:14:20.690 --> 01:14:23.159
BEN! BEN, HURRY!

01:14:23.226 --> 01:14:23.960
WHAT'S THE MATTER?

01:14:24.027 --> 01:14:24.961
IT'S TOOMER!

01:14:25.028 --> 01:14:27.864
HE MADE RED PETTUS
HOLLER TODAY.

01:14:27.931 --> 01:14:29.499
MISS ERLINE
HEARD THEM PETTUS BOYS

01:14:29.566 --> 01:14:32.435
RUNNING THEIR MOUTHS
ABOUT PAYING HIM BACK.

01:14:32.502 --> 01:14:33.803
YOU KNOW
WITH ALL THEM DOGS,

01:14:33.870 --> 01:14:35.939
THEY AIN'T GOING OUT THERE
EMPTY-HANDED.

01:14:36.005 --> 01:14:39.242
YOU GOT TO
BRING HIM BACK TO MY HOUSE.

01:14:39.308 --> 01:14:40.510
IS MOM HOME?

01:14:40.577 --> 01:14:42.445
GONE TO NOVENA
WITH MRS. GRANTHAM.

01:14:42.512 --> 01:14:43.346
WHERE'S DAD?

01:14:43.412 --> 01:14:45.048
AT THE BASE.

01:14:45.114 --> 01:14:49.619
I BETTER CALL HIM
IN CASE I RUN INTO TROUBLE.

01:14:50.687 --> 01:14:52.789
NEGATIVE. NEGATIVE.
NEGATIVE.

01:14:52.856 --> 01:14:55.725
DAD, THEY MIGHT HAVE GUNS.
I'LL TAKE MOM'S CAR.

01:14:55.792 --> 01:14:56.893
NO, I DON'T WANT YOU

01:14:56.960 --> 01:14:59.495
GETTING BETWEEN
THE NIGGERS AND GRITS.

01:14:59.563 --> 01:15:00.697
I'VE GOT TO GO!

01:15:00.764 --> 01:15:02.298
TOOMER CAN TAKE CARE
OF HIMSELF.

01:15:02.365 --> 01:15:04.634
DON'T LEAVE
THAT GODDAMN HOUSE!

01:15:04.701 --> 01:15:08.572
ACKNOWLEDGE.
ACKNOWLEDGE.

01:15:08.638 --> 01:15:11.007
I GAVE YOU
A DIRECT ORDER, HOG.

01:15:11.074 --> 01:15:12.876
ACKNOWLEDGE.

01:15:12.942 --> 01:15:15.812
BEN?

01:15:15.879 --> 01:15:18.081
BEN!

01:15:18.147 --> 01:15:19.783
DON'T ANSWER
WHEN HE CALLS BACK.

01:15:19.849 --> 01:15:22.686
I'M GOING. I'LL GET HIM.

01:15:22.752 --> 01:15:25.922
[TELEPHONE RINGS]

01:15:27.290 --> 01:15:31.460
[RING]

01:15:31.527 --> 01:15:33.262
[RING]

01:15:33.329 --> 01:15:35.599
SON OF A BITCH.

01:15:35.665 --> 01:15:38.668
GIVE ME THE BOTTLE.

01:15:44.741 --> 01:15:46.509
WHERE'S THEM
DAMN DOGS?

01:15:46.576 --> 01:15:48.812
THOUGHT THEY'D BE
ALL OVER US.

01:15:48.878 --> 01:15:49.846
REMEMBER,
DADDY SAID

01:15:49.913 --> 01:15:51.547
YOU'RE JUST
TO SCARE HIM.

01:15:51.615 --> 01:15:56.152
YEAH. I'M GOING TO
SCARE HIM, ALL RIGHT.

01:15:57.086 --> 01:15:59.623
[TO HIMSELF]
COME ON. HA!

01:15:59.689 --> 01:16:03.693
COME ON. OH, YES.

01:16:03.760 --> 01:16:07.597
WE... WE GOT A SURPRISE
FOR Y'ALL, DON'T WE?

01:16:07.664 --> 01:16:09.365
C-C-COME ON.

01:16:09.432 --> 01:16:10.734
HE'S GOT THEM ALL
INSIDE.

01:16:10.800 --> 01:16:12.902
GOOD. THAT WILL
MAKE THINGS EASIER.

01:16:12.969 --> 01:16:16.405
WHAT ARE YOU
GOING TO DO?

01:16:16.472 --> 01:16:20.043
SHOOT ME SOME HOUNDS,
CUZ.

01:16:20.977 --> 01:16:24.313
COME ON NOW.
COME ON.

01:16:25.414 --> 01:16:27.984
COME RIGHT AHEAD, PETTUS.

01:16:28.051 --> 01:16:31.020
YEAH.

01:16:32.221 --> 01:16:33.256
[BUZZING]

01:16:33.322 --> 01:16:34.357
AAH!
AAH!

01:16:35.258 --> 01:16:36.592
HA HA HA HA!

01:16:38.127 --> 01:16:41.665
LET'S GET THE HELL
OUT OF HERE!

01:16:41.731 --> 01:16:45.068
HA HA!

01:16:50.707 --> 01:16:52.441
HA HA HA! NO, SIR.

01:16:52.508 --> 01:16:58.748
I AIN'T GONNA LET THAT TRASH
HURT MY CHILDREN.

01:17:10.459 --> 01:17:13.096
THIS IS PLAIN DUMB,
RED.

01:17:13.162 --> 01:17:15.198
GET THE HELL OUT OF THERE.
LET'S GO HOME.

01:17:15.264 --> 01:17:18.234
I'VE GOT BUSINESS
TO TAKE CARE OF HERE.

01:17:18.301 --> 01:17:20.469
Y'ALL CHICKEN-SHITS
WANT TO GO, THEN GO.

01:17:20.536 --> 01:17:21.237
JUST LEAVE MY CAR.

01:17:21.304 --> 01:17:25.041
COME ON, WILL YOU?

01:17:25.108 --> 01:17:26.609
NOT UNTIL I KICK
THAT SON OF A BITCH'S ASS.

01:17:26.676 --> 01:17:27.944
YOU'RE
ON YOUR OWN.

01:17:28.011 --> 01:17:30.146
I'M TIRED OF FIGHTING
YOUR FIGHTS.

01:17:30.213 --> 01:17:30.947
GO TO HELL.

01:17:31.014 --> 01:17:34.317
SAME TO YOU,
BROTHER.

01:17:36.485 --> 01:17:42.658
[DOGS BARKING]

01:17:42.726 --> 01:17:44.660
HUSH UP! HUSH!

01:17:44.728 --> 01:17:48.898
HUSH! HUSH! HUSH!
THEY'S GONE!

01:18:04.380 --> 01:18:06.349
AIN'T NOBODY OUT THERE.

01:18:06.415 --> 01:18:08.117
THEY'RE GONE, I TOLD YOU.

01:18:08.184 --> 01:18:10.787
GET DOWN.

01:18:18.962 --> 01:18:19.996
I'VE GOT TO
HURT YOU, TOOMER,

01:18:20.063 --> 01:18:22.799
LIKE YOU HURT ME...
EVEN STEVEN.

01:18:22.866 --> 01:18:28.037
AIN'T YOU DONE H-HAD
ENOUGH OF THIS, RED?

01:18:28.104 --> 01:18:30.206
WHY DON'T YOU
GO ON NOW

01:18:30.273 --> 01:18:31.574
BEFORE
SOMETHING HAPPENS?

01:18:31.640 --> 01:18:35.278
YOU MADE THEM PEOPLE
LAUGH AT ME,

01:18:35.344 --> 01:18:38.014
AND NOW I GOT TO
TEACH YOU A LESSON.

01:18:38.081 --> 01:18:41.184
NO!

01:18:53.429 --> 01:18:56.632
I'M GOING TO
GET YOU, RED.

01:18:56.699 --> 01:18:59.535
I'M GOING TO
HURT YOU FOR THAT.

01:18:59.602 --> 01:19:01.838
THAT WAS JUST
THE FIRST ONE.

01:19:01.905 --> 01:19:02.939
TIME I GET DONE,

01:19:03.006 --> 01:19:07.076
YOU AIN'T GONNA
HAVE ONE LEFT.

01:19:07.143 --> 01:19:10.346
GET AWAY!

01:19:18.721 --> 01:19:21.390
JESUS, TOOMER!

01:19:21.457 --> 01:19:26.462
I DIDN'T MEAN TO HIT YOU.
IT WAS THE DOG.

01:19:26.529 --> 01:19:29.532
OH, GOD.

01:19:29.598 --> 01:19:33.136
OH, I DIDN'T MEAN
TO HIT YOU.

01:19:34.137 --> 01:19:37.640
TOOMER,
I DIDN'T MEAN TO HIT...

01:19:37.706 --> 01:19:40.509
TOOMER!

01:19:44.313 --> 01:19:45.348
[GROWLING]

01:19:51.220 --> 01:19:56.359
O.K., RED.
EVEN STEVEN.

01:20:17.713 --> 01:20:19.382
[GUNSHOTS]

01:20:25.221 --> 01:20:26.956
AAH!

01:20:27.023 --> 01:20:33.529
AAH! OH, GOD! AAH...

01:20:33.596 --> 01:20:38.267
AAH...

01:21:17.840 --> 01:21:19.208
TOOMER.

01:21:19.275 --> 01:21:22.678
TOOMER!

01:21:22.745 --> 01:21:25.414
GOD!

01:21:25.481 --> 01:21:28.317
B-B-BEN...

01:21:29.818 --> 01:21:33.322
BEN... BEN...

01:21:33.389 --> 01:21:38.361
IT LOOK LIKE...
WE CAN'T GO SHRIMPING

01:21:38.427 --> 01:21:42.165
ON... ON FRIDAY.

01:21:43.332 --> 01:21:49.505
SURE WE CAN.
YOU PROMISED.

01:21:49.572 --> 01:21:55.611
DEAD MEN DON'T MAKE
TOO GOOD OF FISHERMEN.

01:21:59.715 --> 01:22:02.485
HORSESHIT!

01:22:02.551 --> 01:22:07.991
I'M TAKING YOU
TO THE HOSPITAL.

01:22:10.626 --> 01:22:16.365
DOC TATTEREE'S
GOING TO FIX YOU RIGHT UP.

01:22:16.832 --> 01:22:18.234
UH!

01:22:18.301 --> 01:22:21.370
OH, GOD. I'M SORRY.
I'M SORRY.

01:22:21.437 --> 01:22:23.006
I'M SORRY, MAN.
I'M SORRY.

01:22:23.072 --> 01:22:24.207
JESUS!

01:22:24.273 --> 01:22:26.842
YOU LOST A LOT OF BLOOD,
TOOMER!

01:22:26.909 --> 01:22:28.744
OH, GOD!

01:22:28.811 --> 01:22:31.814
GOD!

01:22:31.880 --> 01:22:35.218
COME ON! DAMN!

01:22:35.851 --> 01:22:38.387
ALL RIGHT.

01:22:39.788 --> 01:22:44.193
B-BEN, HURTS. HURTS.

01:22:44.260 --> 01:22:45.628
I WAS TRYING TO
BE CAREFUL.

01:22:45.694 --> 01:22:49.365
I'M TRYING TO BE CAREFUL.
HONEST, TOOMER. HONEST.

01:22:49.432 --> 01:22:53.036
GOD!

01:22:53.802 --> 01:22:54.970
ALL RIGHT. ALL RIGHT.

01:22:55.038 --> 01:22:56.372
DON'T WORRY
ABOUT A THING.

01:22:56.439 --> 01:23:00.009
THEY'LL FIX YOU UP
IN NO TIME, TOOMER.

01:23:00.076 --> 01:23:03.446
TOOMER?

01:23:03.979 --> 01:23:05.614
TOOMER!

01:23:05.681 --> 01:23:08.551
OH, GOD!

01:23:08.617 --> 01:23:11.554
[STARTS ENGINE]

01:23:51.627 --> 01:23:52.995
DAD.

01:23:53.062 --> 01:23:54.697
DAD.

01:23:54.763 --> 01:23:56.065
TOOMER, DAD...
TOOMER...

01:23:56.132 --> 01:23:58.734
YOU DISOBEYED
A DIRECT ORDER, HOG!

01:23:58.801 --> 01:24:00.936
A DIRECT ORDER
FROM YOUR COMMANDING OFFICER!

01:24:01.003 --> 01:24:02.771
YES, SIR.

01:24:02.838 --> 01:24:04.907
YOU KNEW
YOU'D CATCH HELL FOR IT.

01:24:04.973 --> 01:24:07.376
YOU DID IT ANYWAY.
I WANT TO KNOW WHY.

01:24:07.443 --> 01:24:10.613
BECAUSE I THOUGHT...
I PROMISED ARRABELLE.

01:24:10.679 --> 01:24:13.649
I THOUGHT TOOMER
MIGHT BE IN TROUBLE

01:24:13.716 --> 01:24:14.550
AND...

01:24:14.617 --> 01:24:16.185
AND WHAT?

01:24:16.252 --> 01:24:19.822
AND BECAUSE
I WAS YOUR SON.

01:24:19.888 --> 01:24:21.524
WHAT THE HELL'S
THAT MEAN?

01:24:21.590 --> 01:24:24.293
BECAUSE SANTINI
WOULD HAVE DONE IT.

01:24:24.360 --> 01:24:28.030
WE'RE NOT TALKING
ABOUT ME, GODDAMN IT!

01:24:28.097 --> 01:24:29.232
I'M A MEECHUM.

01:24:29.298 --> 01:24:30.233
A MEECHUM'S
A THOROUGHBRED,

01:24:30.299 --> 01:24:31.500
A WINNER
ALL THE WAY.

01:24:31.567 --> 01:24:34.903
HE CHEWS NAILS.
HE NEVER SURRENDERS.

01:24:34.970 --> 01:24:35.938
HE NEVER GIVES UP.

01:24:36.004 --> 01:24:40.309
YOU DISOBEYED
A DIRECT ORDER!

01:24:41.444 --> 01:24:43.112
I THOUGHT TOOMER
MIGHT BE IN TROUBLE.

01:24:43.179 --> 01:24:46.682
I TOLD YOU HE CAN
TAKE CARE OF HIMSELF.

01:24:46.749 --> 01:24:49.718
YES, SIR.

01:24:49.785 --> 01:24:53.789
THAT'S WHAT
YOU TOLD ME.

01:24:56.058 --> 01:24:57.059
IS THAT HIM
IN THE CAR?

01:24:57.126 --> 01:25:00.629
YES, SIR.

01:25:09.905 --> 01:25:15.311
HEY, TOOMER.
HOW YOU DOING, SPORTS FAN?

01:25:19.215 --> 01:25:22.851
JESUS H. CHRIST.

01:25:35.298 --> 01:25:39.268
BETTER TAKE HIM
TO THE HOSPITAL.

01:25:39.335 --> 01:25:44.340
I'LL GET THE SHERIFF
AND TELL ARRABELLE.

01:25:45.341 --> 01:25:47.443
WHY DIDN'T YOU
TELL ME?

01:25:47.510 --> 01:25:51.380
WHY DIDN'T YOU
SAY SOMETHING?

01:25:51.447 --> 01:25:55.718
NOBODY TELLS YOU
ANYTHING, DAD.

01:26:33.956 --> 01:26:34.957
IT TOOK A LOT OF GUTS

01:26:35.023 --> 01:26:36.024
FOR HIM TO GO
OUT THERE TONIGHT.

01:26:36.091 --> 01:26:37.693
YOU SHOULD BE PROUD.

01:26:37.760 --> 01:26:41.163
VIRG, IF YOU WANT TO
DRINK WITH ME, FINE,

01:26:41.230 --> 01:26:44.800
BUT SKIP THE BILGE,
O.K., SIR?

01:26:44.867 --> 01:26:47.202
O.K.

01:26:47.270 --> 01:26:50.773
O.K.

01:27:01.417 --> 01:27:06.589
VIRG, OLD BUDDY,
I'VE RECENTLY OBSERVED

01:27:06.655 --> 01:27:09.292
THAT FOR CERTAIN
THROWBACKS

01:27:09.358 --> 01:27:11.294
OF THE SPECIES,

01:27:11.360 --> 01:27:13.596
CERTAIN
GUNG-HO DINOSAURS,

01:27:13.662 --> 01:27:18.601
OF WHICH I PROUDLY
NUMBER MYSELF AS ONE,

01:27:18.667 --> 01:27:22.771
BEING A WARRIOR
WITHOUT A WAR...

01:27:22.838 --> 01:27:26.208
HAS ITS PROBLEMS.

01:27:26.275 --> 01:27:27.510
DON'T YOU THINK

01:27:27.576 --> 01:27:33.782
IT'S SMART OF ME
TO OBSERVE THAT?

01:27:34.283 --> 01:27:36.819
BARTENDER.

01:27:36.885 --> 01:27:39.922
BARTENDER.

01:27:41.023 --> 01:27:42.558
[LILLIAN]
YOU BASTARD!

01:27:42.625 --> 01:27:45.694
[BULL]
YOU SHUT UP!
YOU JUST SHUT UP!

01:27:45.761 --> 01:27:47.563
YOU DIDN'T HAVE
A CONSCIENCE, DID YOU?

01:27:47.630 --> 01:27:49.365
YOU KNOW HE DID
WHAT WAS RIGHT!

01:27:49.432 --> 01:27:51.600
YOU DON'T HAVE
ANY CONCERN FOR LIFE!

01:27:51.667 --> 01:27:53.402
YOU DON'T FEEL ANYTHING!

01:27:53.469 --> 01:27:56.905
SHUT UP!
JUST SHUT UP!

01:27:56.972 --> 01:27:59.107
I'M A FIGHTER PILOT,
DON'T YOU UNDERSTAND?

01:27:59.174 --> 01:28:00.042
HOW LONG
DOES IT TAKE YOU

01:28:00.108 --> 01:28:02.077
TO UNDERSTAND THAT?

01:28:02.144 --> 01:28:06.582
TAKE YOUR HANDS
OFF HER!

01:28:07.115 --> 01:28:09.284
COME ON!

01:28:09.352 --> 01:28:11.787
DON'T YOU
TOUCH HIM!

01:28:11.854 --> 01:28:14.923
GET HIM!
GET HIM!

01:28:14.990 --> 01:28:16.625
[ALL YELLING]

01:28:17.526 --> 01:28:21.464
STOP!
STOP IT, DADDY!

01:28:21.530 --> 01:28:24.567
BULL! BULL! BULL!
BULL! BULL! BULL!

01:28:24.633 --> 01:28:27.302
[MATT]
STOP IT!

01:28:27.370 --> 01:28:30.105
STOP IT, DADDY! STOP IT!

01:28:30.172 --> 01:28:33.409
[CRYING]

01:28:59.334 --> 01:29:02.337
SHH...
IT'S ALL RIGHT NOW. HUSH.

01:29:02.405 --> 01:29:08.043
IT'S ALL OVER.
IT'S ALL OVER.
HUSH NOW.

01:29:22.725 --> 01:29:25.461
I'M GETTING WORRIED.

01:29:25.528 --> 01:29:26.695
I HOPE
HE DIES OUT THERE

01:29:26.762 --> 01:29:30.999
WITH THE REST
OF THE SNAKES.

01:29:31.066 --> 01:29:34.770
I WANT YOU TO GO
AND LOOK FOR HIM.

01:29:34.837 --> 01:29:36.639
GIVE ME A GUN,
AND I MIGHT OBLIGE YOU.

01:29:36.705 --> 01:29:40.576
I WANT YOU TO GO BRING
YOUR FATHER HOME, BEN.

01:29:40.643 --> 01:29:41.644
I'M NOT GOING TO
DO THAT, MAMMA.

01:29:41.710 --> 01:29:46.682
YES, YOU ARE.
PLEASE.

01:29:46.749 --> 01:29:48.116
NOW. BEFORE
THE SUN COMES UP

01:29:48.183 --> 01:29:52.655
AND SOMEBODY
FINDS HIM.

01:29:59.361 --> 01:30:02.665
DAD!

01:30:09.337 --> 01:30:12.841
DAD!

01:30:19.882 --> 01:30:22.451
DAD!

01:30:22.518 --> 01:30:25.988
DAD!

01:30:27.422 --> 01:30:28.056
[CLANK]

01:30:28.123 --> 01:30:29.157
AHH...

01:30:29.224 --> 01:30:32.495
[DRUNKENLY]
YES, SIR. YES, SIR. YES, SIR.

01:30:32.561 --> 01:30:36.699
HAPPY BIRTHDAY
TO YOU.

01:30:40.235 --> 01:30:43.171
DEFENSE. DEFENSE.

01:30:43.238 --> 01:30:44.473
[COUGHING]

01:30:44.540 --> 01:30:46.475
WHAT, BUDDY?

01:30:46.542 --> 01:30:48.176
[COUGHS]

01:30:49.545 --> 01:30:53.181
YES, SIR.
YES, SIR. YES, SIR.

01:30:53.248 --> 01:30:55.083
YES, SIR.

01:30:56.552 --> 01:30:59.488
COLONEL W.P. MEECHUM
REPORTING AS ORDERED.

01:30:59.555 --> 01:31:01.690
AS ORDERED, SIR.

01:31:03.091 --> 01:31:06.228
NO, NO, LIL, HONEY.
YOU JUST DON'T UNDERSTAND.

01:31:06.294 --> 01:31:08.631
IT'S DANGEROUS
OUT THERE.

01:31:08.697 --> 01:31:12.701
YOU GENTLE HIM TOO MUCH.
TOO MUCH.

01:31:15.270 --> 01:31:17.205
HE WON'T MAKE IT.

01:31:20.275 --> 01:31:21.710
COLONEL W.P. MEECHUM.

01:31:24.580 --> 01:31:27.215
TERROR OF THE SKIES.

01:31:27.282 --> 01:31:29.151
FATHER.

01:31:29.217 --> 01:31:30.886
DADDY.

01:31:34.590 --> 01:31:36.224
PAPA.

01:31:43.599 --> 01:31:45.033
HEY, YOU GUYS.

01:31:45.100 --> 01:31:47.502
LIL, YOU KIDS,
I'LL TELL YOU WHAT.

01:31:47.570 --> 01:31:51.974
YOU DO MY CARING FOR ME,
DEAL?

01:31:52.040 --> 01:31:53.241
DEAL?

01:31:58.313 --> 01:31:59.748
[CRYING]
DEAL.

01:32:18.466 --> 01:32:19.935
DEAL.

01:32:23.639 --> 01:32:25.273
PAPA.

01:32:27.643 --> 01:32:29.612
PAPA.

01:32:29.678 --> 01:32:31.113
PAPA.

01:32:41.523 --> 01:32:44.660
JUST WATCH OUT.
YOU GOT TO BE FAST...

01:32:46.361 --> 01:32:49.598
'CAUSE THE BOGIES
WILL GET YOU.

01:32:49.665 --> 01:32:51.600
DEFENSE. DEFENSE.

01:32:51.667 --> 01:32:54.803
YOU GOT TO WORK
THAT DEFENSE, BENNY.

01:32:57.673 --> 01:33:00.609
YOU GOT TO
WATCH YOUR SIX.

01:33:00.676 --> 01:33:03.679
NOW YOU GUARD ME.

01:33:06.381 --> 01:33:08.684
O.K., BUDDY.

01:33:11.687 --> 01:33:14.823
BENNY, YOU GUARD ME,
WILL YOU?

01:33:25.400 --> 01:33:26.835
DAD.

01:33:30.706 --> 01:33:32.641
HEY, I'M SICK. JESUS.

01:33:32.708 --> 01:33:34.643
I'M SICK, BOY.

01:33:34.710 --> 01:33:36.344
[RETCHES]

01:33:51.727 --> 01:33:53.662
COME ON, DAD.

01:33:53.729 --> 01:33:57.365
LET'S GO HOME.
YOU AND ME.

01:34:09.244 --> 01:34:13.381
DAD. I THINK
I UNDERSTAND NOW, DAD.

01:34:22.758 --> 01:34:24.893
I LOVE YOU, DAD.

01:34:28.764 --> 01:34:31.700
DID YOU HEAR
WHAT I SAID?

01:34:31.767 --> 01:34:33.936
I LOVE YOU!

01:34:34.937 --> 01:34:36.705
DID YOU HEAR ME?

01:34:36.772 --> 01:34:39.507
DID YOU HEAR ME,
SANTINI?

01:34:39.574 --> 01:34:43.411
WATCH YOUR SIX NOW.
GUARD ME, DAD. GUARD ME.

01:34:43.478 --> 01:34:45.213
GUARD ME.
HERE I COME.

01:34:45.280 --> 01:34:47.716
WHOA. COME ON.
TAKE ANOTHER SWING, DAD.

01:34:47.783 --> 01:34:49.885
COME ON, DAD.
I'M RIGHT HERE.

01:34:49.952 --> 01:34:52.220
THIS BOGY'S
GOT YOU ZEROED.

01:34:52.287 --> 01:34:53.956
COME AND GET ME.
COME AND GET ME.

01:34:54.022 --> 01:34:56.725
THIS BOGY, DAD.
THIS ONE.

01:34:56.792 --> 01:35:00.428
I LOVE YOU, DAD.
WHOA.

01:35:00.495 --> 01:35:02.230
I LOVE YOU,

01:35:02.297 --> 01:35:05.734
AND THERE'S NOTHING
YOU'RE GOING TO DO ABOUT IT.

01:35:05.801 --> 01:35:08.937
I LOVE YOU, DAD.
I LOVE YOU.

01:35:13.809 --> 01:35:16.111
COME ON. LOOK OUT.

01:35:16.178 --> 01:35:17.813
LOOK OUT.

01:35:20.816 --> 01:35:22.450
[YELLING]

01:35:27.856 --> 01:35:29.992
THE DEAD BUG IS DOWN.

01:35:31.827 --> 01:35:33.461
AH!

01:35:33.528 --> 01:35:35.297
SO COME ON.

01:35:38.700 --> 01:35:40.135
LET'S GO HOME.

01:35:42.537 --> 01:35:43.972
LET'S GO HOME.

01:35:50.879 --> 01:35:52.314
SOUTH CAROLINA?

01:35:52.380 --> 01:35:53.481
COLUMBIA.

01:35:53.548 --> 01:35:54.582
NORTH CAROLINA?

01:35:54.649 --> 01:35:55.383
GRITSVILLE.

01:35:55.450 --> 01:35:56.251
RALEIGH.

01:35:56.318 --> 01:35:58.086
O.K. GOOD. URUGUAY?

01:35:58.153 --> 01:36:00.388
THAT'S WHERE
YOU WERE STUCK LAST TIME.

01:36:00.455 --> 01:36:02.390
BEAUFORT.

01:36:02.457 --> 01:36:03.491
MONIDEVEO?

01:36:03.558 --> 01:36:04.793
MONTEVIDEO.

01:36:04.860 --> 01:36:06.361
AND AFGHANISTAN?

01:36:06.428 --> 01:36:08.496
KABUL.

01:36:08.563 --> 01:36:10.765
TA-DA.

01:36:10.833 --> 01:36:13.501
HEY, LOOKING GOOD,
SPORTS FANS.

01:36:13.568 --> 01:36:14.769
WHERE'S MARY ANNE?

01:36:14.837 --> 01:36:16.171
GETTING DRESSED.

01:36:16.238 --> 01:36:18.206
SHE'S BEEN GETTING
DRESSED FOR THREE DAYS.

01:36:18.273 --> 01:36:19.908
SHE REALLY LIKES
THE GOWN YOU BOUGHT.

01:36:19.975 --> 01:36:21.009
IT WAS TOO EXPENSIVE.

01:36:21.076 --> 01:36:24.179
ONLY THE BEST
FOR MY HOGS.

01:36:24.246 --> 01:36:25.547
LET YOUR MOTHER COMPLETE
THE INSPECTION.

01:36:27.950 --> 01:36:29.885
MADAM,
HOW DO I LOOK?

01:36:29.952 --> 01:36:31.453
LIKE A PRINCE.
TURN AROUND.

01:36:31.519 --> 01:36:32.888
LIKE
A QUEEN.

01:36:32.955 --> 01:36:35.457
STOP THAT. PRACTICE THOSE
STEPS ONCE MORE, O.K.?

01:36:35.523 --> 01:36:37.092
REMEMBER,
LEFT FOOT FIRST.

01:36:37.159 --> 01:36:41.396
♪ DUM DA DA DUM DUM,
DOOP DOOP, DOOP DOOP ♪

01:36:41.463 --> 01:36:44.599
NOW, DON'T LOOK DOWN.
LOOK UP AT ME.

01:36:44.666 --> 01:36:46.601
ONE, TWO. ONE...

01:36:46.668 --> 01:36:47.769
NOT SO CLOSE.

01:36:47.836 --> 01:36:49.271
SO CLOSE, HUH?

01:36:49.337 --> 01:36:53.775
OH, ANY GIRL WOULD BE PROUD
TO GO TO THE PROM WITH YOU.

01:36:53.842 --> 01:36:55.010
WOULDN'T SHE?

01:36:55.077 --> 01:36:56.211
MAMMA. MAMMA.

01:36:56.278 --> 01:36:57.612
HONESTLY.

01:36:57.679 --> 01:36:59.614
YOU JUST LOOK
SO WONDERFUL.

01:36:59.681 --> 01:37:01.616
MARY ANNE
ACTS LIKE SHE'S MAD

01:37:01.683 --> 01:37:02.918
I ASKED HER.

01:37:02.985 --> 01:37:04.920
[WOLF WHISTLE]

01:37:04.987 --> 01:37:09.057
OH, YOU LOOK ABSOLUTELY
STUNNING, SUGAR.

01:37:09.124 --> 01:37:12.060
I DIDN'T KNOW YOU WERE
SO STACKED, SPORTS FANS.

01:37:12.127 --> 01:37:14.029
HUSH, BULL.
MY GOD.

01:37:14.096 --> 01:37:16.631
HOW SICKO SEXUAL
CAN YOU GET?

01:37:16.698 --> 01:37:18.666
WAIT UNTIL
I GET MY KODAK.

01:37:18.733 --> 01:37:20.135
YOU LOOK BEAUTIFUL,
MARY ANNE.

01:37:20.202 --> 01:37:23.138
I'M SO TIRED OF PEOPLE
ADMIRING MY BEAUTY,

01:37:23.205 --> 01:37:26.841
BEING HOMECOMING QUEEN
FOR TWO YEARS IN A ROW.

01:37:26.909 --> 01:37:29.311
YOU?
A HOMECOMING QUEEN?

01:37:29.377 --> 01:37:30.445
HA!

01:37:30.512 --> 01:37:34.216
GO FIND A TOADSTOOL
TO SIT UNDER, GRUB.

01:37:34.282 --> 01:37:34.983
OLD FOUR EYES

01:37:35.050 --> 01:37:35.817
GETS A KNUCKLE SANDWICH

01:37:35.884 --> 01:37:37.119
FOR THAT ONE.

01:37:37.185 --> 01:37:39.955
GET TOGETHER NOW.
HOLD STILL.

01:37:40.022 --> 01:37:43.125
WHERE
ARE YOUR GLASSES?

01:37:43.191 --> 01:37:46.261
THEY DETRACT
FROM MY HEAVENLY BEAUTY.

01:37:46.328 --> 01:37:46.962
SMILE!

01:37:47.029 --> 01:37:48.263
BETTER
HURRY.

01:37:48.330 --> 01:37:50.565
YOUR RESERVATIONS ARE AT 1900.

01:37:50.632 --> 01:37:51.733
FLYING TONIGHT?

01:37:51.799 --> 01:37:53.101
ROUTINE NIGHT FLIGHT.

01:37:53.168 --> 01:37:55.470
GIVE ME A KISS.
GET GOING.

01:37:55.537 --> 01:37:56.838
YOU LOOK BEAUTIFUL.

01:37:56.905 --> 01:37:58.173
BYE.

01:38:00.275 --> 01:38:01.476
SEE YOU AT BREAKFAST,
SPORTS FANS.

01:38:01.543 --> 01:38:02.945
HAVE A NICE TIME.

01:38:03.011 --> 01:38:05.180
[MATT]
MARY ANNE.

01:38:05.247 --> 01:38:06.514
WHAT?

01:38:06.581 --> 01:38:07.482
YOU...

01:38:07.549 --> 01:38:09.651
YOU LOOK NICE.

01:38:09.717 --> 01:38:10.652
THANK YOU.

01:38:10.718 --> 01:38:11.686
AW...

01:38:11.753 --> 01:38:14.389
HAVE FUN,
SPORTS FANS.

01:38:18.393 --> 01:38:19.427
GOOD-BYE.

01:38:22.830 --> 01:38:25.200
[BAND PLAYING MOON RIVER]

01:38:32.374 --> 01:38:35.310
CAN YOU BELIEVE
DAD BOUGHT ME THIS DRESS?

01:38:35.377 --> 01:38:39.014
HE CAN BE SO CHILDISHLY
SENTIMENTAL SOMETIMES.

01:38:39.081 --> 01:38:41.383
ISN'T THIS RIDICULOUS?

01:38:51.393 --> 01:38:55.497
GET READY,
SPORTS FANS.

01:38:55.563 --> 01:38:56.131
ONE, TWO, THREE...

01:38:56.198 --> 01:38:58.333
MY BIG-CITY MOVE.

01:38:58.400 --> 01:39:00.502
MY DARLING, THAT'S AN
ENORMOUS BOOGER IN YOUR NOSE.

01:39:11.213 --> 01:39:13.648
♪ YOU KNOW
YOU TWIST SO FINE ♪

01:39:13.715 --> 01:39:15.150
♪ TWIST SO FINE ♪

01:39:15.217 --> 01:39:19.021
♪ COME ON AND TWIST
A LITTLE CLOSER... ♪

01:39:28.196 --> 01:39:32.634
I AM SANTINI,
THE GREAT SANTINI.

01:39:32.700 --> 01:39:37.139
I COME AT NIGHT FROM THE MOON,
FROM BEHIND THE CLOUDS...

01:39:37.205 --> 01:39:39.474
UNANNOUNCED.

01:39:39.541 --> 01:39:42.144
OUT OF THE BLACK,
WATCH OUT!

01:39:42.210 --> 01:39:44.512
WATCH OUT!
HEE HEE HEE!

01:39:45.913 --> 01:39:49.517
HA HA HA HA!
HEY HEY!

01:40:55.283 --> 01:40:57.085
BEAUFORT APPROACH.

01:40:57.152 --> 01:40:59.921
WEREWOLF ONE INBOUND
TO SAND DOLLAR FIX.

01:40:59.987 --> 01:41:01.123
REQUEST TACAN APPROACH.

01:41:01.189 --> 01:41:02.424
ROGER, WEREWOLF ONE.

01:41:02.490 --> 01:41:06.928
DESCEND AND MAINTAIN
FLIGHT LEVEL 240.

01:41:06.994 --> 01:41:09.431
CLEARED FOR
TACAN PENETRATION.

01:41:23.745 --> 01:41:27.081
BEAUFORT APPROACH,
THIS IS WEREWOLF ONE.

01:41:27.149 --> 01:41:28.950
I HAVE A FIRE WARNING LIGHT.

01:41:29.016 --> 01:41:31.219
I'M DECLARING EMERGENCY.

01:41:31.286 --> 01:41:32.387
REQUEST
IMMEDIATE PENETRATION.

01:41:32.454 --> 01:41:36.958
ROGER, TURN RIGHT
TO 330.

01:41:37.024 --> 01:41:38.860
CLEARED TO 2,000 FEET.

01:41:41.829 --> 01:41:43.465
[WARNING BUZZER]

01:41:47.034 --> 01:41:49.971
COAST CONTROL,
WEREWOLF ONE.

01:41:50.037 --> 01:41:52.974
STEADY ON THE HEADING 330.

01:41:53.040 --> 01:41:54.709
REQUEST GCA PICKUP.

01:41:54.776 --> 01:41:56.478
ROGER, WEREWOLF ONE.

01:42:04.486 --> 01:42:06.988
COME ON, SWEETHEART,
SETTLE DOWN.

01:42:07.054 --> 01:42:08.723
DON'T DO THIS TO ME.

01:42:10.458 --> 01:42:12.727
MAYDAY, WEREWOLF ONE,
I'M ON FIRE!

01:42:12.794 --> 01:42:15.197
SKIP THE GCA.
I'M COMING STRAIGHT IN.

01:42:20.868 --> 01:42:23.338
THIS THING IS COMING APART.
I GOT TO GET OUT.

01:42:23.405 --> 01:42:25.106
PUNCH OUT. PUNCH OUT.

01:42:25.173 --> 01:42:27.209
[COUGHING]

01:42:30.077 --> 01:42:31.613
FORGET IT.
I'M OVER THE TOWN.

01:42:31.679 --> 01:42:34.516
I'M GOING TO TRY TO GET
THIS THING TO THE WATER.

01:42:41.189 --> 01:42:42.690
I LOST YOUR BOY, GUNNY.

01:42:42.757 --> 01:42:46.027
TOWER, ANY FIRES
NEAR THE RUNWAY?

01:42:46.093 --> 01:42:47.329
NEGATIVE.

01:42:47.395 --> 01:42:49.030
ANGEL FIVE,
ANGEL FIVE,

01:42:49.096 --> 01:42:50.598
WE HAVE
AN AIRCRAFT DOWN

01:42:50.665 --> 01:42:54.135
APPROXIMATELY FIVE MILES
EAST OF RUNWAY 32.

01:42:54.202 --> 01:42:56.037
[KNOCKING ON DOOR]

01:42:56.103 --> 01:42:58.039
MOM? MOM?

01:42:58.105 --> 01:43:00.475
COME ON IN, SUGAR.

01:43:00.542 --> 01:43:02.477
WHAT ARE YOU DOING UP
SO EARLY?

01:43:02.544 --> 01:43:04.145
I THINK SOMETHING'S
HAPPENED TO DAD.

01:43:04.212 --> 01:43:07.048
COLONEL VARNEY AND COLONEL
HEDGEPATH ARE DOWNSTAIRS.

01:43:07.114 --> 01:43:08.383
WHAT?

01:43:25.433 --> 01:43:27.269
[INDISTINCT VOICES]

01:43:59.667 --> 01:44:00.635
BEN...

01:44:00.702 --> 01:44:02.470
YES, MAMMA?

01:44:02.537 --> 01:44:06.608
GO AND WAKE UP
THE CHILDREN.

01:44:08.175 --> 01:44:10.312
TELL THEM
TO COME DOWN HERE.

01:44:12.280 --> 01:44:15.249
I HAVE SOMETHING TO TELL
YOU ABOUT YOUR DADDY.

01:44:15.317 --> 01:44:18.653
YES, MA'AM.

01:44:18.720 --> 01:44:20.755
GO ON NOW.

01:44:31.699 --> 01:44:33.335
[SOB]

01:44:35.202 --> 01:44:37.439
[MUFFLED SOB]

01:44:37.505 --> 01:44:39.441
HOLY MARY, MOTHER OF GOD,

01:44:39.507 --> 01:44:41.208
PRAY FOR US SINNERS NOW
AND AT THE HOUR OF OUR DEATH.

01:44:41.275 --> 01:44:42.710
AMEN.

01:44:42.777 --> 01:44:46.013
GLORY BE TO THE FATHER
AND THE SON AND THE HOLY GHOST.

01:44:46.080 --> 01:44:49.551
AS IT WAS IN THE BEGINNING,
IS NOW, AND EVER SHALL BE.

01:44:49.617 --> 01:44:52.620
WORLD WITHOUT END. AMEN.

01:44:55.222 --> 01:44:57.659
NOW I WANT TO SAY SOMETHING.

01:44:59.026 --> 01:45:02.664
TOMORROW WILL BE
VERY HARD ON ALL OF US.

01:45:04.031 --> 01:45:07.168
BUT THE MEECHUM FAMILY
WILL CONDUCT ITSELF HONORABLY

01:45:07.234 --> 01:45:08.970
AT THE FUNERAL.

01:45:09.036 --> 01:45:12.407
WE WILL NOT CRY IN PUBLIC.

01:45:12.474 --> 01:45:14.175
BULL WOULD NOT
HAVE LIKED IT.

01:45:14.241 --> 01:45:16.243
HE WOULD WANT US
TO BE STRONG.

01:45:16.310 --> 01:45:18.279
OUR GRIEF WILL BE PRIVATE.

01:45:18.346 --> 01:45:22.116
NOW, IF YOU WISH TO CRY,
YOU CRY NOW.

01:45:22.183 --> 01:45:23.518
CRY HERE AT THE HOUSE,

01:45:23.585 --> 01:45:27.389
CRY WITH EACH OTHER
AND WITH OUR FRIENDS,

01:45:27.455 --> 01:45:30.191
BUT TOMORROW
THERE WILL BE NO TEARS.

01:45:30.257 --> 01:45:34.496
YOU WILL REMEMBER AT ALL TIMES

01:45:34.562 --> 01:45:38.199
THAT YOU ARE
THE CHILDREN OF BULL MEECHUM,

01:45:38.265 --> 01:45:40.402
AND YOU WILL ACT ACCORDINGLY.

01:45:40.468 --> 01:45:43.405
CAN'T I JUST SNIFFLE
ONCE OR TWICE?

01:45:43.471 --> 01:45:45.507
DON'T YOU DARE
SMART-MOUTH ME

01:45:45.573 --> 01:45:48.710
AT A TIME LIKE THIS,
MARY ANNE.

01:45:53.581 --> 01:45:56.217
YOU AND YOUR BROTHER TAKE
THE CHILDREN AND GO UPSTAIRS

01:45:56.283 --> 01:45:58.052
SO I CAN SAY
MY PRAYERS IN PEACE.

01:45:58.119 --> 01:45:59.721
YES, MA'AM.

01:45:59.787 --> 01:46:01.723
COME ON, KIDS.

01:46:28.049 --> 01:46:30.251
MAMMA.

01:46:30.317 --> 01:46:32.487
AIN'T YOU GOING TO BED?

01:46:32.554 --> 01:46:36.558
IN A WHILE, SUGAR.
IN A WHILE.

01:46:36.624 --> 01:46:38.693
CAN'T YOU SLEEP?

01:46:41.629 --> 01:46:43.898
COME AND SIT DOWN.

01:46:48.836 --> 01:46:50.472
[SIGH]

01:46:54.842 --> 01:46:56.277
MAMMA.

01:46:56.343 --> 01:46:58.279
HMM?
YES, DARLING?

01:46:58.345 --> 01:47:00.782
I GOT TO TELL YOU
SOMETHING.

01:47:00.848 --> 01:47:02.283
WHAT?

01:47:02.349 --> 01:47:06.588
I... I... I...

01:47:06.654 --> 01:47:11.292
USED TO PRAY...

01:47:11.358 --> 01:47:14.796
FOR HIS PLANE TO CRASH.

01:47:14.862 --> 01:47:17.499
I REALLY DID.

01:47:18.866 --> 01:47:20.502
AND...

01:47:22.369 --> 01:47:24.606
AND I JUST...

01:47:24.672 --> 01:47:27.609
KEEP THINKING THAT...

01:47:27.675 --> 01:47:30.311
ONE OF THOSE PRAYERS...

01:47:30.377 --> 01:47:35.617
WAS UP THERE
FLOATING AROUND, AND HE...

01:47:35.683 --> 01:47:39.521
HE ACCIDENTALLY
RAN INTO IT.

01:47:41.889 --> 01:47:43.825
NO, IT WASN'T.

01:47:43.891 --> 01:47:45.627
MAMMA, MAMMA,

01:47:45.693 --> 01:47:48.630
MAMMA, I FEEL SO TERRIBLE...

01:47:48.696 --> 01:47:52.634
THAT HE H-H-HAD TO DIE

01:47:52.700 --> 01:47:56.137
FOR ME TO BE FREE.

01:47:56.203 --> 01:48:00.642
NOW, LISTEN.
IT WAS NOT HIS DYING.

01:48:00.708 --> 01:48:03.545
LISTEN TO ME NOW.

01:48:04.712 --> 01:48:06.147
YOU WERE FREE

01:48:06.213 --> 01:48:09.651
THE NIGHT THAT
YOU WENT TO HELP TOOMER.

01:48:09.717 --> 01:48:11.553
NOW LOOK AT ME.

01:48:13.721 --> 01:48:16.558
YOU KNOW THAT'S TRUE,
DON'T YOU?

01:48:17.925 --> 01:48:19.561
HMM?

01:48:25.733 --> 01:48:27.368
ALL RIGHT, NOW.

01:48:27.434 --> 01:48:28.870
SHH.

01:48:28.936 --> 01:48:30.371
[SNIFFLES]

01:48:30.437 --> 01:48:31.873
SHH.

01:48:36.243 --> 01:48:39.380
HE DIED BECAUSE
HE STAYED WITH HIS PLANE

01:48:39.446 --> 01:48:42.083
TILL IT WAS CLEAR
OF THE TOWN...

01:48:42.149 --> 01:48:47.889
BECAUSE HE WAS A TRUE MARINE
AND BECAUSE HE CARED.

01:48:47.955 --> 01:48:52.627
I WANT TO TELL YOU,
BEN, MARY ANNE,

01:48:52.694 --> 01:48:56.564
MATTHEW, KAREN,
AND LILLIAN

01:48:56.631 --> 01:48:59.300
THAT I'LL LIKE THE WORLD LESS
WITHOUT BULL.

01:48:59.366 --> 01:49:03.671
IT WILL BE A DULLER,
MORE COLORLESS PLACE.

01:49:05.539 --> 01:49:07.742
WE'LL ALL REMEMBER HIM,

01:49:07.809 --> 01:49:10.578
AND WE'LL HONOR THAT MEMORY.

01:49:10.645 --> 01:49:12.614
DETAIL, ATTENTION!

01:49:13.781 --> 01:49:15.617
[SHOUTING COMMANDS]

01:49:21.488 --> 01:49:25.392
READY! AIM! FIRE!

01:49:25.459 --> 01:49:27.595
AIM! FIRE!

01:49:27.662 --> 01:49:29.430
[GUNSHOTS]

01:49:29.496 --> 01:49:31.599
AIM! FIRE!

01:49:31.666 --> 01:49:34.669
DETAIL, ATTENTION!

01:49:34.736 --> 01:49:36.638
[SHOUTING COMMANDS]

01:49:44.511 --> 01:49:46.213
[PLAYS TAPS]

01:50:27.554 --> 01:50:29.991
[JETS APPROACHING]

01:50:40.868 --> 01:50:42.870
THERE'S ONE MISSING.

01:50:42.937 --> 01:50:44.672
THAT'S WHERE
PAPA SHOULD BE.

01:51:00.587 --> 01:51:02.389
[SIGH]

01:51:02.456 --> 01:51:03.691
GOOD-BYE, HOUSE.

01:51:03.758 --> 01:51:06.393
GOOD-BYE,
BEAUFORT.

01:51:20.274 --> 01:51:22.710
MATT, DID OKRA
GO TO THE BATHROOM?

01:51:22.777 --> 01:51:24.712
HOW SHOULD I KNOW?

01:51:24.779 --> 01:51:26.680
DID YOU ALL GO
TO THE BATHROOM?

01:51:26.748 --> 01:51:29.851
YOU WANT AN AFFIDAVIT?

01:51:29.917 --> 01:51:33.921
WE'RE NOT GOING TO BE STOPPING
EVERY 15 SECONDS.

01:51:35.790 --> 01:51:38.525
WHY DO WE ALWAYS HAVE
TO LEAVE AT 3 A.M.?

01:51:38.592 --> 01:51:41.362
BECAUSE THERE'S NO TRAFFIC,
AND WE MAKE BETTER TIME,

01:51:41.428 --> 01:51:42.730
SO STOP COMPLAINING.

01:51:42.797 --> 01:51:45.232
I'LL NEVER SEE MARY,
HELEN, OR ALICE AGAIN.

01:51:45.299 --> 01:51:47.534
WE'LL BE BACK, SUGAR.
WE'LL COME BACK FOR A VISIT.

01:51:47.601 --> 01:51:49.703
THAT'S WHAT YOU SAID ABOUT
CHERRY POINT AND NEW RIVER.

01:51:49.771 --> 01:51:51.739
HUSH NOW, HUSH.

01:51:51.806 --> 01:51:53.440
[STARTS ENGINE]

01:52:04.318 --> 01:52:06.754
[BEN]
♪ HE HAS LOOSED
THE FATEFUL LIGHTNING ♪

01:52:06.821 --> 01:52:08.756
♪ OF HIS TERRIBLE,
SWIFT SWORD ♪

01:52:08.823 --> 01:52:13.560
♪ HIS TRUTH IS MARCHING ON ♪

01:52:13.627 --> 01:52:15.763
[CHILDREN]
♪ OH, I WISH I WERE
IN THE LAND OF COTTON ♪

01:52:15.830 --> 01:52:17.765
♪ OLD TIMES THERE
ARE NOT FORGOTTEN ♪

01:52:17.832 --> 01:52:19.767
♪ LOOK AWAY, LOOK AWAY ♪

01:52:19.834 --> 01:52:21.568
♪ LOOK AWAY, DIXIELAND ♪

01:52:21.635 --> 01:52:24.806
♪ I WISH I WAS IN DIXIE,
AWAY, AWAY... ♪
